#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/basiq.rst:32
msgid "Business banking data sharing"
msgstr "Partage des données bancaires professionnelles"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/basiq.rst:34
msgid ""
"Under Australia's Consumer Data Right (CDR) regime, sharing business banking "
"data requires an explicit **opt-in**. You can ask your bank to enable this "
"opt-in, but the steps vary by bank. Refer to Basiq's `CDR documentation "
"<https://api.basiq.io/docs/connecting-business-accounts-via-cdr>`_ for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Selon le régime australien Consumer Data Right (CDR), le partage des données "
"bancaires professionnelles nécessite une adhésion explicite (**opt-in**). "
"Vous pouvez demander à votre banque d'activer cette adhésion, mais les "
"étapes varient selon les banques. Consultez la `documentation CDR de Basiq "
"<https://api.basiq.io/docs/connecting-business-accounts-via-cdr>`_ pour plus "
"d'informations."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/basiq.rst:40
msgid ""
"To see how Odoo manages your financial data and how to access, update, or "
"delete it, read the `Odoo finance privacy policy page <https://"
"production.odoofin.com/privacy#basiq>`_."
msgstr ""
"Pour voir comment Odoo gère vos données financières et comment y accéder, "
"les mettre à jour ou les supprimer, consultez la `page de politique de "
"confidentialité Odoo Finance <https://production.odoofin.com/privacy#basiq>"
"`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/basiq.rst:44
