"third-party :guilabel:`Provider`."
msgstr ""
"Lors de la connexion à la banque souhaitée, s'assurer que Ponto est "
"sélectionné comme :guilabel:`Provider` tiers."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/ponto.rst:60
msgid ""
"Select the account(s) to grant Ponto access to account balances and "
