msgid ""
":ref:`SEPA Credit Transfer (SCT) is activated <accounting/sepa_payments/"
"sct>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Le virement SEPA (SCT) est activé <accounting/sepa_payments/sct>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/ponto.rst:82
msgid ""
":ref:`The SEPA Credit Transfer payment method has been added to the bank "
"journal <accounting/sepa_payments/sct_configuration>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`La méthode de paiement Virement SEPA a été ajoutée au journal bancaire "
