#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/bank/bank_synchronization/ponto.rst:84
msgid ""
":ref:`The vendor's bank account has been marked as trusted <accounting/batch/"
"bank-accounts>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Le compte bancaire du fournisseur a été marqué comme fiable "
