msgid ":doc:`Taxes <taxes>` (if applicable)"
msgstr ":doc:`Taxes <taxes>` (le cas échéant)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:57
msgid ""
"To access the product catalog and view all items in an organized display, "
"click :doc:`Catalog </applications/essentials/product_catalog>`. When the "
"products and quantities are selected, click :guilabel:`Back to Invoice` to "
"return to the invoice; the selected catalog items will appear in the invoice "
"lines."
msgstr ""
"Pour accéder au catalogue de produits et afficher tous les articles dans un "
"affichage organisé, cliquer sur :doc:`Catalogue </applications/essentials/"
"product_catalog>`. Lorsque les produits et les quantités sont sélectionnés, "
"cliquer sur :guilabel:`Retour à la facture` pour revenir à la facture ; les "
"articles du catalogue sélectionnés apparaîtront dans les lignes de facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:63
msgid ""
"To display the total amount of the invoice in words, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and activate "
"the :guilabel:`Total amount of invoice in letters` option."
msgstr ""
"Pour afficher le montant total de la facture en lettres, allez "
"dans :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Configuration --> Paramètres` et "
"activez l'option :guilabel:`Montant total de la facture en lettres`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:67
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Journal Items` tab displays the accounting entries created. "
"Additional invoice information such as the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Reference`, :guilabel:`Payment Reference`, :doc:`Fiscal Positions <taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>`, :doc:`Incoterms <customer_invoices/incoterms>`, and more "
"can be added or modified in the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab."
msgstr ""
"L'onglet :guilabel:`Écritures comptables` affiche les écritures comptables "
"créées. Des informations supplémentaires sur la facture telles que "
"la :guilabel:`Référence client`, la :guilabel:`Référence de paiement`, "
"les :doc:`Positions fiscales <taxes/fiscal_positions>`, les :doc:`Incoterms "
"<customer_invoices/incoterms>` et plus encore peuvent être ajoutées ou "
"modifiées dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Autres infos`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:73
msgid ""
"Odoo initially creates invoices in :guilabel:`Draft` status. Draft invoices "
"have no accounting impact until they are :ref:`confirmed <accounting/invoice/"
"confirmation>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo crée initialement les factures avec le statut :guilabel:`Brouillon`. "
"Les factures en brouillon n'ont aucun impact comptable jusqu'à ce qu'elles "
"soient :ref:`confirmées <accounting/invoice/confirmation>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:77
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/overview.rst:47
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:82
msgid "Invoice confirmation"
msgstr "Confirmation de facture"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:84
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` when the invoice is completed. The invoice's "
"status changes to :guilabel:`Posted`, and a journal entry is generated based "
"on the invoice configuration. On confirmation, Odoo assigns each invoice a "
"unique number from a defined :doc:`sequence <customer_invoices/sequence>`."
msgstr ""
"Cliquez sur :guilabel:`Confirmer` lorsque la facture est complète. Le statut "
"de la facture passe à :guilabel:`Comptabilisée`, et une pièce comptable est "
"générée en fonction de la configuration de la facture. Lors de la "
"confirmation, Odoo attribue à chaque facture un numéro unique issu "
"d'une :doc:`séquence <customer_invoices/sequence>` définie."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:90
msgid ""
"Once confirmed, an invoice can no longer be updated. Click :guilabel:`Reset "
"to draft` if changes are needed."
msgstr ""
"Une fois confirmée, une facture ne peut plus être mise à jour. Cliquez "
"sur :guilabel:`Réinitialiser en brouillon` si des modifications sont "
"nécessaires."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:92
msgid ""
"If required, invoices and other journal entries can be locked once posted "
"using the :ref:`Secure posted entries with hash <data-inalterability/"
"restricted>` feature."
msgstr ""
"Si nécessaire, les factures et autres écritures comptables peuvent être "
"verrouillées une fois comptabilisées à l'aide de la "
"fonctionnalité :ref:`Sécuriser les écritures comptabilisées avec hachage "
"<data-inalterability/restricted>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:98
msgid "Invoice sending"
msgstr "Envoi de la facture"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:100
msgid ""
"To set a preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method for a customer, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers --> Customers` and select the "
"customer. In the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab of the contact form, select the "
"preferred :guilabel:`Invoice sending` method in the :guilabel:`Customer "
"Invoices` section."
msgstr ""
"Pour définir une méthode d':guilabel:`Envoi de facture` préférée pour un "
"client, aller à :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Clients --> Clients` et "
"sélectionner le client. Dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Comptabilité` du formulaire "
"de contact, sélectionner la méthode d':guilabel:`Envoi de facture` préférée "
"dans la section :guilabel:`Factures clients`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:106
msgid ""
"Sending letters in Odoo requires :doc:`In-App Purchase (IAP) <../../"
"essentials/in_app_purchase>` credit or tokens."
msgstr ""
"Envoyer des lettres dans Odoo nécessite des crédits ou jetons :doc:`Achat In-"
"App (IAP) <../../essentials/in_app_purchase>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:109
msgid ""
"To send the invoice to the customer, navigate back to the invoice record and "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Pour envoyer la facture au client, revenir à l'enregistrement de facture et "
"suivre ces étapes :"

