":ref:`Plusieurs factures <accounting/invoice/sending-multiple-invoices>` "
"peuvent également être envoyées en lot via Peppol."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:168
msgid ""
"Set the preferred :ref:`Invoice sending <accounting/invoice/sending>` method "
"for a customer to :guilabel:`by Peppol` in the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` "
"section of the customer form's :guilabel:`Accounting` tab."
msgstr ""
"Définissez la :ref:`méthode d’envoi <accounting/invoice/sending>` préférée "
"des factures d’un client sur :guilabel:`via Peppol` dans la "
"section :guilabel:`Factures client` de l’onglet :guilabel:`Comptabilité` de "
"la fiche client."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:172
msgid ""
"The status is updated to :guilabel:`Done` once the invoices have been "
"successfully delivered to the contact's access point."
msgstr ""
"Le statut est mis à jour sur :guilabel:`Terminé` une fois que les factures "
"ont été livrées avec succès au point d’accès du contact."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:176
msgid ""
"To manually trigger the scheduled action used to check the invoices' status, "
"go to the Accounting dashboard and click :guilabel:`Fetch Peppol invoice "
"status` on the corresponding sales journal."
msgstr ""
"Pour déclencher manuellement l'action planifiée utilisée pour vérifier le "
"statut des factures, aller dans le tableau de bord Comptabilité et cliquer "
"sur :guilabel:`Récupérer le statut des factures Peppol` sur le journal de "
"ventes correspondant."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:0
msgid "Fetch invoice Peppol status"
msgstr "Récupérer le statut Peppol de la facture"

