msgid "Receive vendor bills"
msgstr "Recevoir les factures fournisseurs"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:188
msgid ""
"New documents received via Peppol are checked multiple times a day. Received "
"documents are automatically imported into the purchase journal set in "
"the :guilabel:`PEPPOL Electronic Invoicing` section, and corresponding "
"vendor bills are created as drafts and appear in the vendor bills list view."
msgstr ""
"Les nouveaux documents reçus via Peppol sont vérifiés plusieurs fois par "
"jour. Les documents reçus sont automatiquement importés dans le journal "
"d'achat défini dans la section :guilabel:`Facturation électronique PEPPOL`, "
"et les factures fournisseurs correspondantes sont créées en tant que "
"brouillons et apparaissent dans la vue liste des factures fournisseurs."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing.rst:194
msgid ""
"To manually trigger the scheduled action to retrieve incoming Peppol "
