#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:11
msgid "Legal framework for e-invoicing in Estonia"
msgstr "Cadre juridique de la facturation électronique en Estonie"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Estonia, businesses must comply with e-invoicing regulations to ensure "
"secure, authentic, and storable transactions. The main legal framework "
"governing e-invoicing in Estonia is the `Accounting Act <https://"
"www.riigiteataja.ee/en/eli/ee/514052021001/consolide/current>`_ and its "
"provisions related to e-invoicing, which align with `EU Directive 2014/55/EU "
"<https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_ "
"on e-invoicing in public procurement. Since 2019, :abbr:`B2G (business-to-"
"government)` transactions must use electronic invoices via Estonia's Rik's e-"
"Invoicing System, the government's platform for public sector e-invoicing. "
"Estonia is also part of the Peppol network, which ensures standardized cross-"
"border e-invoicing across Europe. Additionally, the use of e-invoicing is "
"encouraged for B2B transactions, promoting better transparency, efficiency, "
"and compliance with VAT requirements."
msgstr ""
"En Estonie, les entreprises doivent se conformer aux réglementations en "
"matière de facturation électronique pour garantir des transactions "
"sécurisées, authentiques et stockables. Le principal cadre juridique "
"régissant la facturation électronique en Estonie est la `loi sur la "
"comptabilité <https://www.riigiteataja.ee/en/eli/ee/514052021001/consolide/"
"current>`_ et ses dispositions relatives à la facturation électronique, qui "
"s'alignent sur la `directive européenne 2014/55/UE <https://eur-"
"lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32014L0055>`_ concernant la "
"facturation électronique dans les marchés publics. Depuis 2019, les "
"transactions :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` doivent utiliser des "
"factures électroniques via le système de facturation électronique Rik's "
"d'Estonie, la plateforme gouvernementale pour la facturation électronique du "
"secteur public. L'Estonie fait également partie du réseau Peppol, qui "
"garantit une facturation électronique transfrontalière standardisée à "
"travers l'Europe. De plus, l'utilisation de la facturation électronique est "
"encouragée pour les transactions B2B, favorisant une meilleure transparence, "
"efficacité et conformité aux exigences en matière de TVA."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:24
msgid "Compliance with Estonian e-invoicing regulations"
msgstr ""
"Conformité aux réglementations estoniennes en matière de facturation "
"électronique"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Supported formats**: Odoo supports standard e-invoice formats, such as XML "
"in :abbr:`UBL (Universal Business Language)` format, which is fully "
"compatible with Estonia's Rik’s e-Invoicing System for public procurement "
"transactions. Additionally, Odoo enables seamless transmission of e-invoices "
"through platforms connected to the Peppol network, ensuring compliance with "
"Estonian and EU e-invoicing standards."
msgstr ""
"**Formats pris en charge** : Odoo prend en charge les formats de facture "
"électronique standard, tels que le XML au format :abbr:`UBL (Universal "
"Business Language)`, qui est entièrement compatible avec le système de "
"facturation électronique Rik's d'Estonie pour les transactions de marchés "
"publics. De plus, Odoo permet la transmission transparente des factures "
"électroniques via des plateformes connectées au réseau Peppol, garantissant "
"la conformité aux normes estoniennes et européennes de facturation "
"électronique."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:34
msgid ""
"**Secure storage and retrival**: In accordance with Estonian regulations to "
"store invoices for a minimum of seven years, Odoo securely archives all "
"invoices in a tamper-proof system, making them easily retrievable during "
"audits."
msgstr ""
"**Stockage et récupération sécurisés** : Conformément aux réglementations "
"estoniennes exigeant de conserver les factures pendant au moins sept ans, "
"Odoo archive de manière sécurisée toutes les factures dans un système "
"inviolable, les rendant facilement récupérables lors des audits."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:37
msgid ""
"**Automatic VAT calculation and reporting**: Odoo Invoicing automates VAT "
"calculations and ensures invoices are formatted to meet Denmark’s legal "
"requirements for :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` and B2B transactions, "
"helping businesses compliant with local tax laws."
msgstr ""
"**Calcul et déclaration automatiques de la TVA** : Odoo Facturation "
"automatise les calculs de TVA et garantit que les factures sont formatées "
"pour répondre aux exigences légales du Danemark pour les "
"transactions :abbr:`B2G (business-to-government)` et B2B, aidant les "
"entreprises à se conformer aux lois fiscales locales."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/estonia.rst:43
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of Estonian e-invoicing laws and how Odoo "
