"If :guilabel:`Included in Price` is :guilabel:`Tax Excluded`, the "
"computation is :math:`\\text{tax amount} = \\text{sales price} \\times "
"\\text{tax rate}`."
msgstr ""
"Si :guilabel:`compris dans le prix` est :guilabel:`hors taxes`, le calcul "
"est :math:`\\text{montant de la taxe} = \\text{prix de vente} \\times "
"\\text{taux de taxe}`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/tax_computation.rst:71
msgid ""
"A product has a sales price of $1000, and we apply a "
"10% :guilabel:`Percentage of Price` tax that is :guilabel:`Tax Excluded`. We "
"then have:"
msgstr ""
"Un produit a un prix de vente de 1 000 $ et nous appliquons une "
"taxe :guilabel:`pourcentage du prix` de 10 % qui est :guilabel:`hors taxes`. "
"Nous avons alors :"

