#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:116
msgid ""
"France's `electronic invoicing reform <https://www.impots.gouv.fr/"
"professionnel/je-passe-la-facturation-electronique>`_ *(reforme de la "
"facturation électronique)* impacts all VAT-registered French companies, and "
"is being rolled out in two phases:"
msgstr ""
"La `réforme de la facturation électronique <https://www.impots.gouv.fr/"
"professionnel/je-passe-la-facturation-electronique>`_ française impacte "
"toutes les entreprises françaises assujetties à la TVA, et se déploie en "
"deux phases :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:121
msgid "From **September 1, 2026**:"
msgstr "À partir du **1er septembre 2026** :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:123
msgid ""
"every company must be able to receive domestic B2B e-invoices via "
"*plateformes agréées* (approved platforms) :ref:`(e-invoicing) "
"<localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-einvoicing>`"
msgstr ""
"toute entreprise doit être en mesure de recevoir des factures électroniques "
"B2B domestiques via des *plateformes agréées* :ref:`(facturation "
"électronique) <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-einvoicing>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:125
msgid ""
"large enterprises (GE) and mid-sized enterprises (ETI) must send domestic "
"B2B e-invoices :ref:`(e-invoicing) <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-"
"elec-einvoicing>` and must submit data to the tax authorities about certain "
"operations, such as B2C and cross-border B2B operations :ref:`(e-reporting) "
"<localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`"
msgstr ""
"les grandes entreprises (GE) et les entreprises de taille intermédiaire "
"(ETI) doivent envoyer des factures électroniques B2B nationales :ref:`"
"(facturation électronique) <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-"
"einvoicing>` et doivent transmettre des données aux autorités fiscales "
"concernant certaines opérations, telles que les opérations B2C et B2B "
"transfrontalières :ref:`(e-reporting) <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-"
"elec-reporting>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:130
msgid ""
"From **September 1, 2027**, every company, including small and medium-sized "
"enterprises (PME) and micro-enterprises are subject to the same :ref:`e-"
"invoicing <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-einvoicing>` "
"and :ref:`e-reporting <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>` "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"À partir du **1er septembre 2027**, toutes les entreprises, y compris les "
"petites et moyennes entreprises (PME) et les micro-entreprises sont soumises "
"aux mêmes exigences de :ref:`facturation électronique <localizations/france/"
"e-invoicing-fac-elec-einvoicing>` et d':ref:`e-reporting <localizations/"
"france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:135
msgid ""
"Odoo is officially certified as a *plateforme agréée* (approved platform) on "
"the e-invoicing network. It supports the receipt of documents in various "
"formats (Facture-X, UBL, and CII) and the sending of documents exclusively "
"in UBL format."
msgstr ""
"Odoo est officiellement certifié en tant que *plateforme agréée* sur le "
"réseau de facturation électronique. Il prend en charge la réception de "
"documents dans différents formats (Facture-X, UBL et CII) et l'envoi de "
"documents exclusivement au format UBL."

