#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:266
msgid ""
"To send a debit or credit note to Infile, first create the :ref:`debit "
"<accounting/credit_notes/issue-debit-note>` or :ref:`credit note <accounting/"
"credit_notes/issue-credit-note>`."
