msgstr "Configuration indienne"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/india.rst:67
msgid ""
"In :menuselection:`Settings --> Users & Companies --> Companies`, add "
"your :guilabel:`PAN` and :guilabel:`GSTIN`. The PAN is essential for "
"determining the type of taxpayer, while GSTIN is required for generating e-"
