"When creating a new invoice, open the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab and set "
"the :guilabel:`Payment QR-code` option to :guilabel:`QRIS`."
msgstr ""
"Lors de la création d'une nouvelle facture, ouvrir "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Autres informations` et définir l'option :guilabel:`QR-"
