#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:80
msgid ":guilabel:`Tax System`: the tax system under which the company falls;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Système fiscal` : le système fiscal de la société ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "Company information to be provided"
msgstr "Informations sur l'entreprise à fournir"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:88
msgid "Taxes configuration"
msgstr "Configuration des taxes"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:90
msgid ""
"Many of the e-invoicing features are implemented using Odoo's tax system. As "
"such, taxes must be properly configured to generate invoices correctly and "
"handle other billing use cases."
msgstr ""
"De nombreuses fonctionnalités de facturation électronique sont implémentées "
"en utilisant le système de taxes d'Odoo. Par conséquent, les taxes doivent "
"être correctement configurées pour générer les factures correctement et "
"gérer d'autres cas d'usage de facturation."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:93
msgid ""
"The **Italian** localization contains predefined **examples** of taxes for "
"various purposes."
msgstr ""
"La localisation **italienne** contient des **exemples** prédéfinis de taxes "
"à diverses fins."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:98
msgid "Tax exemption"
msgstr "Exonération de taxe"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:100
msgid ""
"The use of sale taxes that amount to **zero percent** (0%) is required by "
"Italian authorities to keep track of the exact :guilabel:`Tax Exemption Kind "
"(Natura)` and :guilabel:`Law Reference` that justify the exemption operated "
"on an invoice line."
msgstr ""
"L'utilisation de taxes de vente d'un montant de **zéro pour cent** (0 %) est "
"requise par les autorités italiennes pour garder trace du :guilabel:`Type "
"d'exonération fiscale (Natura)` exact et de la :guilabel:`Référence légale` "
"qui justifient l'exonération appliquée sur une ligne de facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:105
msgid ""
"The export tax in the EU can be used as reference (`0% EU`, invoice label "
"`00eu`). It can be found under :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration "
"--> Taxes`. Exports are exempt from VAT, and therefore, they "
"require :guilabel:`Exoneration` kind and :guilabel:`Law Reference` filled in."
msgstr ""
"La taxe d'exportation dans l'UE peut être utilisée comme référence (`0% EU`, "
"libellé de facture `00eu`). Elle se trouve sous :menuselection:`Comptabilité "
"--> Configuration --> Taxes`. Les exportations sont exonérées de TVA, et par "
"conséquent, elles nécessitent que le type :guilabel:`Exonération` et "
"la :guilabel:`Référence légale` soient remplis."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "Tax Exemption Settings"
msgstr "Paramètres d'exonération fiscale"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:113
msgid ""
"There are many :guilabel:`Tax Exemption Kind (Natura)` and :guilabel:`Law "
"Reference` codes. Make sure you check the latest version available to get "
"the latest information on:"
msgstr ""
"Il existe de nombreux codes :guilabel:`Type d'exonération fiscale (Natura)` "
"et :guilabel:`Référence légale`. Assurez-vous de vérifier la dernière "
"version disponible pour obtenir les informations les plus récentes sur :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:116
msgid ""
"`Italian authorities documentation <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/"
"portale/web/guest/aree-tematiche/fatturazione-elettronica>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Documentation des autorités italiennes <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/"
"portale/web/guest/aree-tematiche/fatturazione-elettronica>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:117
msgid ""
"`Official guide on Tax exemption <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/portale/"
"documents/20143/451259/Guida_compilazione-FE-Esterometro-"
"V_1.9_2024-03-05.pdf/67fe4c2d-1174-e8de-f1ee-cea77b7f5203>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Guide officiel sur l'exonération fiscale <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/"
"portale/documents/20143/451259/Guida_compilazione-FE-Esterometro-"
"V_1.9_2024-03-05.pdf/67fe4c2d-1174-e8de-f1ee-cea77b7f5203>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:120
msgid ""
"If you need to use a different kind of exoneration, go "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Taxes`, select a similar "
"tax, then click on the cog icon and select :guilabel:`Duplicate`. In "
"the :guilabel:`Advanced Options` tab, add the :guilabel:`Exoneration` "
"and :guilabel:`Law Reference`. To confirm click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Pour utiliser un autre type d'exonération, aller "
"dans :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Configuration --> Taxes`, sélectionner "
"une taxe similaire, puis cliquer sur l'icône d'engrenage et "
"sélectionner :guilabel:`Dupliquer`. Dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Options "
"avancées`, ajouter l':guilabel:`Exonération` et la :guilabel:`Référence "
"légale`. Pour confirmer, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Enregistrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:126
msgid ""
"**Rename** your taxes in the :guilabel:`Name` field according to "
"their :guilabel:`Exoneration` to differentiate them easily."
msgstr ""
"**Renommez** vos taxes dans le champ :guilabel:`Nom` en fonction de "
"leur :guilabel:`Exonération` pour les identifier facilement."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:132
msgid "Reverse charge"
msgstr "Autoliquidation"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:134
msgid ""
"The **reverse charge** mechanism is a VAT rule that shifts the liability to "
"pay VAT from the supplier to the customer. The customers pay the VAT "
"*themselves* to the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` instead. There are "
"different types:"
msgstr ""
"Le mécanisme de l'**autoliquidation** est une règle de TVA qui transfère la "
"responsabilité du paiement de la TVA du fournisseur au client. Les clients "
"paient la TVA *eux-mêmes* à l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` à la "
"place. Il existe différents types :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Internal Reverse Charge` (for domestic sales)"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Autoliquidation interne` (pour les ventes domestiques)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"The VAT responsibility is shifted to the buyer for certain categories of "
"products and services."
msgstr ""
"La responsabilité de la TVA est transférée à l'acheteur pour certaines "
"catégories de produits et services."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`External Reverse Charge` (for intra-EU sales)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Autoliquidation externe` (pour les ventes intracommunautaires)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"VAT is due in the country of the delivery or in the country where the "
"service is performed. When the buyer is itself an Italian business, then the "
"EU offers a mechanism that allows the seller to transfer his responsibility "
"to the buyer."
msgstr ""
"La TVA est due dans le pays de livraison ou dans le pays où le service est "
"effectué. Lorsque l'acheteur est lui-même une entreprise italienne, l'UE "
"offre un mécanisme qui permet au vendeur de transférer sa responsabilité à "
"l'acheteur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:148
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:586
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:230
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_arab_emirates.rst:204
msgid "Invoices"
msgstr "Factures clients"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:150
msgid ""
"**Reverse-charged** customer invoices show no VAT amount, but the :abbr:`AdE "
"(Agenzia delle Entrate)` requires the seller to specify the :guilabel:`Tax "
"Exemption` reason and the :guilabel:`Law Reference` that enable the reverse-"
"charge mechanism. Odoo provides a set of special 0% taxes that can be "
"assigned to each reverse-charged invoice lines, representing the most "
"commonly used configurations."
msgstr ""
"Les factures clients en **autoliquidation** n'affichent aucun montant de "
"TVA, mais l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` exige que le vendeur "
"spécifie la raison de l':guilabel:`Exonération fiscale` et la "
":guilabel:`Référence légale` qui permet le mécanisme d'autoliquidation. Odoo "
"fournit un ensemble de taxes spéciales à 0 % qui peuvent être attribuées à "
"chaque ligne de facture en autoliquidation, représentant les configurations "
"les plus couramment utilisées."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:161
msgid ""
"Italian companies subjected to Reverse Charge must send the information in "
"the bill received to the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`."
msgstr ""
"Les entreprises italiennes soumises à l'autoliquidation doivent envoyer les "
"informations de la facture reçue à l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:165
msgid ""
"Self-reported VAT XML files must be issued and sent to the :abbr:`AdE "
"(Agenzia Delle Entrate)` for reverse charged bills."
msgstr ""
"Les fichiers XML de TVA auto-déclarée doivent être émis et envoyés à "
"l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle Entrate)` pour les factures fournisseurs en "
"autoliquidation."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:168
msgid ""
"When creating a vendor bill, **reverse charge** taxes are available to be "
"added in the :guilabel:`Taxes` field. You can check which taxes are "
"available by going to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> "
"Taxes`, you can see that the 10% Goods and 22% Services taxes are activated, "
"among others. Due to the automated configuration of the Italian fiscal "
"position, these are automatically activated in the tax list."
msgstr ""
"Lors de la création d'une facture fournisseur, les taxes "
"d'**autoliquidation** sont disponibles pour être ajoutées dans le "
"champ :guilabel:`Taxes`. Vous pouvez vérifier quelles taxes sont disponibles "
"en allant dans :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Configuration --> Taxes`. "
"Vous pouvez voir que les taxes de 10 % sur les biens et 22 % sur les "
"services sont activées, entre autres. En raison de la configuration "
"automatisée de la position fiscale italienne, celles-ci sont automatiquement "
"activées dans la liste des taxes."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:177
msgid "Tax grids"
msgstr "Grilles fiscales"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:179
msgid ""
"The Italian localization has a specific :ref:`tax grid <tax-returns/tax-"
"grids>` section for **reverse charge** taxes. These tax grids are "
"identifiable by the :guilabel:`VJ` tag, and can be found by going "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Tax Return`."
msgstr ""
"La localisation italienne dispose d'une section :ref:`grille de taxes <tax-"
"returns/tax-grids>` spécifique pour les taxes en **autoliquidation**. Ces "
"grilles de taxes sont identifiables par le tag :guilabel:`VJ` et peuvent "
"être trouvées en allant dans :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Rapports --> "
"Déclaration de TVA`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "Reverse charge tax grid from the VJ section of the Tax Declaration"
msgstr ""
"Grille fiscale d'autoliquidation de la section VJ de la déclaration fiscale"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:192
msgid ""
"Make sure all the Italian-specific e-invoicing modules are :ref:`installed "
"<general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Assurez-vous que tous les modules de facturation électronique italiens "
"spécifiques sont :ref:`installés <general/install>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:194
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` is the :doc:`electronic invoicing "
"<../accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing>` system used in "
"Italy. It enables the sending and receiving of electronic invoices to and "
"from customers. The documents must be in an XML :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data "
"Interchange)` format called **FatturaPA** and formally validated by the "
"system before being delivered."
msgstr ""
"Le :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` est le système de :doc:`facturation "
"électronique <../accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing>` utilisé "
"en Italie. Il permet l'envoi et la réception de factures électroniques vers "
"et depuis les clients. Les documents doivent être dans un format XML "
":abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)` appelé **FatturaPA** et "
"formellement validés par le système avant d'être livrés."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:200
msgid ""
"To be able to receive invoices and notifications, the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)` service must be notified that the user's files need to be "
"sent to Odoo and processed on their behalf. To do so, you must set up "
"Odoo's :guilabel:`Destination Code` on the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle "
"Entrate)` portal."
msgstr ""
"Pour pouvoir recevoir des factures et des notifications, le service "
":abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` doit être informé que les fichiers de "
"l'utilisateur doivent être envoyés à Odoo et traités en son nom. Pour ce "
"faire, vous devez configurer le :guilabel:`Code Destinataire` d'Odoo sur le "
"portail de l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle Entrate)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:205
msgid ""
"Go to `Italian authorities portal <https://ivaservizi.agenziaentrate.gov.it/"
"portale>`_ and authenticate;"
msgstr ""
"Aller sur le `portail des autorités italiennes <https://"
"ivaservizi.agenziaentrate.gov.it/portale>`_ et s'authentifier ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:207
msgid "Go to section :guilabel:`Fatture e Corrispettivi`;"
msgstr "Accédez à la section :guilabel:`Fatture e Corrispettivi` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:208
msgid ""
"Set the user as Legal Party for the VAT number you wish to configure the "
"electronic address;"
msgstr ""
"Définissez l'utilisateur comme Partie légale pour le numéro de TVA dont vous "
"souhaitez configurer l'adresse électronique ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:209
msgid ""
"In :menuselection:`Servizi Disponibili --> Fatturazione Elettronica --> "
"Registrazione dell’indirizzo telematico dove ricevere tutte le fatture "
"elettroniche`, insert Odoo's :guilabel:`Destination Code` `K95IV18`, and "
"confirm."
msgstr ""
"Dans :menuselection:`Servizi Disponibili --> Fatturazione Elettronica --> "
"Registrazione dell'indirizzo telematico dove ricevere tutte le fatture "
"elettroniche`, insérer le :guilabel:`Code destinataire` d'Odoo `K95IV18`, et "
"confirmer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:216
msgid "EDI Mode and authorization"
msgstr "Mode EDI et autorisation"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:218
msgid ""
"Since the files are transmitted through Odoo's server before being sent to "
"the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` or received by your database, you "
"need to authorize Odoo to process your files from your database. To do so, "
"go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and scroll "
"to the :guilabel:`Italian Electronic Invoicing` section."
msgstr ""
"Comme les fichiers sont transmis via le serveur d'Odoo avant d'être envoyés "
"au :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` ou reçus par votre base de données, "
"vous devez autoriser Odoo à traiter vos fichiers depuis votre base de "
"données. Pour ce faire, allez dans :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> "
"Configuration --> Paramètres` et faites défiler jusqu'à la section "
":guilabel:`Facturation électronique italienne`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:223
msgid "There are three modes available:"
msgstr "Trois modes sont disponibles :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Demo`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Démo`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"This mode simulates an environment in which invoices are sent to the "
"government. In this mode, invoices need to be *manually* downloaded as XML "
"files and uploaded to the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`'s website."
msgstr ""
"Ce mode simule un environnement dans lequel les factures sont envoyées au "
"gouvernement. Dans ce mode, les factures doivent être téléchargées "
"*manuellement* sous forme de fichiers XML et téléversées sur le site web de "
"l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Test (experimental)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Test (expérimental)`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"This mode sends invoices to a non-production (i.e., test) service made "
"available by the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`. Saving this change "
"directs all companies on the database to use this configuration."
msgstr ""
"Ce mode envoie les factures à un service hors production (c'est-à-dire de "
"test) mis à disposition par l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`. "
"L'enregistrement de ce changement dirige toutes les entreprises de la base "
"de données vers l'utilisation de cette configuration."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Official`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Officiel`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"This is a production mode that sends your invoices directly to "
"the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`."
msgstr ""
"Il s'agit d'un mode de production qui envoie vos factures directement à "
"l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:237
msgid ""
"Once a mode is selected, you need to accept the **terms and conditions** by "
"ticking :guilabel:`Allow Odoo to process invoices`, and "
"then :guilabel:`Save`. You can now record your transactions in Odoo "
"Accounting."
msgstr ""
"Une fois que vous avez sélectionnez un mode, vous devez accepter les "
"**conditions générales** en cochant :guilabel:`Autoriser Odoo à traiter les "
"factures`, et puis en cliquant sur :guilabel:`Enregistrer`. Vous pouvez "
"désormais enregistrer vos transactions dans Odoo Comptabilité."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:242
msgid ""
"Selecting either :guilabel:`Test (experimental)` or :guilabel:`Official` is "
"**irreversible**. For example, once in :guilabel:`Official` mode, it is not "
"possible to select :guilabel:`Test (experimental)` or :guilabel:`Demo`. We "
"recommend creating a **separate database** for testing purposes only."
msgstr ""
"La sélection de :guilabel:`Test (expérimental)` ou :guilabel:`Officiel` est "
"**irréversible**. Par exemple, une fois en mode :guilabel:`Officiel`, il "
"n'est pas possible de sélectionner :guilabel:`Test (expérimental)` ou "
":guilabel:`Démo`. Nous recommandons de créer une **base de données "
"distincte** uniquement à des fins de test."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:248
msgid ""
"When in :guilabel:`Test (Experimental)` mode, all invoices sent *must* have "
"a partner using one of the following fake :guilabel:`Destination Code` given "
"by the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle Entrate)`: `0803HR0` - `N8MIMM9` - "
"`X9XX79Z`. Any real production :guilabel:`Codice Destinario` of your "
"customers will not be recognized as valid by the test service."
msgstr ""
"En mode :guilabel:`Test (Expérimental)`, toutes les factures envoyées "
"*doivent* avoir un partenaire utilisant l'un des faux :guilabel:`Code "
"Destinataire` suivants fournis par l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle Entrate)` : "
"`0803HR0` - `N8MIMM9` - `X9XX79Z`. Tout véritable :guilabel:`Codice "
"Destinario` de production de vos clients ne sera pas reconnu comme valide "
"par le service de test."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "Electronic document invoicing settings"
msgstr "Paramètres de facturation électronique des documents"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:259
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:677
msgid "Process"
msgstr "Traiter"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:261
msgid ""
"The submission of invoices to the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` for "
"Italy is an electronic process used for the mandatory transmission of tax "
"documents in XML format between companies and the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle "
"Entrate)` to reduce errors and verify the correctness of operations."
msgstr ""
"La soumission de factures au :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` pour "
"l'Italie est un processus électronique utilisé pour la transmission "
"obligatoire de documents fiscaux au format XML entre les entreprises et "
"l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` afin de réduire les erreurs et de "
"vérifier l'exactitude des opérations."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:266
msgid ""
"You can check the current status of an invoice by the :guilabel:`SdI State` "
"field. The XML file is attached to the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez vérifier le statut actuel d'une facture via le "
"champ :guilabel:`État SdI`. Le fichier XML est joint à la facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "EDI system architecture"
msgstr "Architecture du système EDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:275
msgid "XML Documents creation"
msgstr "Création de documents XML"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:277
msgid ""
"Odoo generates the required XML files as attachments to invoices in the "
"`FatturaPA` format required by the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`. Once "
"the invoices needed are selected, click the :guilabel:`Send` button."
msgstr ""
"Odoo génère les fichiers XML requis en tant que pièces jointes aux factures "
"au format `FatturaPA` exigé par l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`. Une "
"fois les factures nécessaires sélectionnées, cliquer sur le "
"bouton :guilabel:`Envoyer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:281
msgid ""
"When the pop-up window opens there is a selection of actions that can be "
"taken. :guilabel:`Generate XML File` generates the attachments."
msgstr ""
"Lors de l'ouverture de la fenêtre contextuelle, plusieurs actions sont "
"disponibles. :guilabel:`Générer le fichier XML` génère les pièces jointes."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:284
msgid ""
"The XML file as well as the PDF once can be found attached to the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Le fichier XML ainsi que le PDF se trouvent en pièces jointes de la facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "EDI Attachments"
msgstr "Pièces jointes EDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:289
msgid "After choosing the desired actions, click :guilabel:`send`."
msgstr ""
"Après avoir choisi les actions souhaitées, cliquer sur :guilabel:`envoyer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:294
msgid "Submission to SDI"
msgstr "Envoi au SDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:296
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Send to Tax Agency` sends the attachment to "
"the :guilabel:`Proxy Server`, which gathers all requests and then forwards "
"them via a WebServices channel to the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. "
"Check the sending status of the invoice through the :guilabel:`Check "
"Sending` button at the top of the invoice's view."
msgstr ""
"L'option :guilabel:`Envoyer à l'administration fiscale` envoie la pièce "
"jointe au :guilabel:`Serveur proxy`, qui rassemble toutes les demandes puis "
"les transmet via un canal WebServices au :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)"
"`. Vérifier le statut d'envoi de la facture via le bouton "
":guilabel:`Vérifier l'envoi` en haut de la vue de la facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:304
msgid "Processing by SDI"
msgstr "Traitement par le SDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:306
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` receives the document and verifies "
"for any errors. At this stage, the invoice is in the :guilabel:`SdI "
"Processing` state, as shown on the invoice. The invoice also gets assigned "
"a :guilabel:`FatturaPA Transaction` number that is shown in "
"the :guilabel:`Electronic Invoicing` tab. The checks may take variable time, "
"ranging from a few seconds up to a day, depending on the queue of invoices "
"sent throughout Italy."
msgstr ""
"Le :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` reçoit le document et vérifie les "
"éventuelles erreurs. À ce stade, la facture est dans l'état :guilabel:`SdI "
"Processing`, comme indiqué sur la facture. La facture se voit également "
"attribuer un numéro de :guilabel:`FatturaPA Transaction` qui est affiché "
"dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Electronic Invoicing`. Les vérifications peuvent "
"prendre un temps variable, allant de quelques secondes à un jour, selon la "
"file d'attente des factures envoyées dans toute l'Italie."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "Check Sending button and Sdi Processing state"
msgstr "Vérifier le bouton d'envoi et l'état de traitement SDI"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:318
msgid "Acceptance"
msgstr "Acceptation"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:320
msgid ""
"If the document is valid, it is recorded and considered fiscally valid by "
"the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`, which will proceed with archiving "
"in :guilabel:`Substitute Storage (Conservazione Sostitutiva)` if explicitly "
"requested on the Agency's portal."
msgstr ""
"Si le document est valide, il est enregistré et considéré comme fiscalement "
"valide par l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`, qui procédera à "
"l'archivage dans :guilabel:`Substitute Storage (Conservazione Sostitutiva)` "
"si cela est explicitement demandé sur le portail de l'Agence."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:325
msgid ""
"Odoo does not offer the `Conservazione Sostitutiva <https://www.agid.gov.it/"
"index.php/it/piattaforme/conservazione>`_ requirements. Other providers "
"and :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` supply free and certified storage to "
"meet the specifications requested by law."
msgstr ""
"Odoo n'offre pas les exigences de `Conservazione Sostitutiva <https://"
"www.agid.gov.it/index.php/it/piattaforme/conservazione>`_. D'autres "
"fournisseurs et l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` fournissent un "
"stockage gratuit et certifié pour répondre aux spécifications requises par "
"la loi."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:330
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` :guilabel:`Destination Code` "
"attempts to forward the invoice to the customer at the provided address, "
"whether it is a `PEC` email address or a :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)` :guilabel:`Destination Code` for their ERP's WebServices "
"channels. A maximum of 6 attempts are made every 12 hours, so even if "
"unsuccessful, this process can take up to three days. The invoice status "
"is :guilabel:`Accepted by SDI, Forwarding to Partner`."
msgstr ""
"Le :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` :guilabel:`Destination Code` tente "
"de transmettre la facture au client à l'adresse fournie, qu'il s'agisse "
"d'une adresse électronique `PEC` ou d'un :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)"
"` :guilabel:`Destination Code` pour les canaux WebServices de leur ERP. Un "
"maximum de 6 tentatives sont effectuées toutes les 12 heures, donc même en "
"cas d'échec, ce processus peut prendre jusqu'à trois jours. Le statut de la "
"facture est :guilabel:`Accepted by SDI, Forwarding to Partner`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:339
msgid "Possible Rejection"
msgstr "Rejet possible"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:341
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` may find inaccuracies in the "
"compilation, possibly even formal ones. In this case, the invoice is in "
"the :guilabel:`SDI Rejected` state. The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`'s observations are inserted at the top of the Invoice tab. To "
"resolve the issue, it is sufficient to delete the attachments of the "
"invoice, return the invoice to :guilabel:`Draft`, and fix the errors. Once "
"the invoice is ready, it can be resent."
msgstr ""
"Le :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` peut trouver des inexactitudes dans "
"la compilation, éventuellement même formelles. Dans ce cas, la facture est "
"dans l'état :guilabel:`SDI Rejected`. Les observations du :abbr:`SdI "
"(Sistema di Interscambio)` sont insérées en haut de l'onglet Facture. Pour "
"résoudre le problème, il suffit de supprimer les pièces jointes de la "
"facture, de ramener la facture à l'état :guilabel:`Draft` et de corriger les "
"erreurs. Une fois la facture prête, elle peut être renvoyée."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:348
msgid ""
"To regenerate the XML, both the XML attachment and the PDF report must be "
"deleted, so that they are then regenerated together. This ensures that both "
"always contain the same data."
msgstr ""
"Pour régénérer le XML, la pièce jointe XML et le rapport PDF doivent tous "
"deux être supprimés, afin qu'ils soient ensuite régénérés ensemble. Cela "
"garantit qu'ils contiennent toujours les mêmes données."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:None
msgid "EDI Rejected State"
msgstr "État EDI rejeté"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:357
msgid "Forwarding Completed"
msgstr "Transfert terminé"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:359
msgid ""
"The invoice has been delivered to the customer; however, you can still send "
"a copy to the customer in PDF via email or post. Its status "
"is :guilabel:`Accepted by SDI, Delivered to Partner`."
msgstr ""
"La facture a été livrée au client ; vous pouvez toutefois encore envoyer une "
"copie au client au format PDF par e-mail ou courrier. Son statut "
"est :guilabel:`Accepté par SDI, livré au partenaire`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:362
msgid ""
"If the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` cannot contact your customer, "
"they may not be registered on the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` "
"portal. In this case, just make sure to send the invoice in PDF via email or "
"by mail. The invoice is then in the :guilabel:`Accepted by SDI, Partner "
"Delivery Failed` state."
msgstr ""
"Si le :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` ne peut pas contacter votre "
"client, celui-ci n'est peut-être pas enregistré sur le portail de "
"l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`. Dans ce cas, assurez-vous simplement "
"d'envoyer la facture en PDF par courriel ou par courrier. La facture est "
"alors dans l'état :guilabel:`Accepted by SDI, Partner Delivery Failed`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:370
msgid "Tax Integration"
msgstr "Intégration fiscale"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:372
msgid ""
"When you receive a vendor bill, either from :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`, from paper or from an imported XML file, the Tax Agency "
"might request that you send some tax information integration back to "
"the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. It happens when a transaction "
"that was tax exempt becomes taxable for any reason."
msgstr ""
"Lorsque vous recevez une facture fournisseur, soit du :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`, soit sur papier, soit à partir d'un fichier XML importé, "
"l'Agence des impôts peut demander que vous renvoyiez certaines informations "
"d'intégration fiscale au :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. Cela se "
"produit lorsqu'une transaction qui était exonérée de taxe devient imposable "
"pour une raison quelconque."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:378
msgid "Here is a non-exhaustive list:"
msgstr "Voici une liste non exhaustive :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`"
msgstr ":ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"As a buyer, you have to pay taxes on what you buy and integrate tax "
"information. :guilabel:`Reverse Charge` taxes."
msgstr ""
"En tant qu'acheteur, vous devez payer les taxes sur vos achats et intégrer "
"les informations fiscales. Taxes :guilabel:`Autoliquidation`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":ref:`localizations/italy/split-payment`"
msgstr ":ref:`localizations/italy/split-payment`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"As a :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business buyer, you have to pay "
"taxes and integrate tax information. Be sure that you replace "
"the :guilabel:`0% Sale Taxes` on the vendor bill you received with the "
"correct :guilabel:`Split Payment` taxes."
msgstr ""
"En tant qu'acheteur professionnel :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)`, vous "
"devez payer des taxes et intégrer les informations fiscales. Assurez-vous de "
"remplacer les :guilabel:`0% Sale Taxes` sur la facture fournisseur que vous "
"avez reçue par les taxes correctes de :guilabel:`Split Payment`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ":guilabel:`Self Consumption`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Autoconsommation`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid ""
"When, as a business owner, you use an asset that you bought for business for "
"personal reasons instead, you have to pay those taxes you originally "
"deducted as a business cost for it."
msgstr ""
"Lorsque, en tant que chef d'entreprise, vous utilisez une immobilisation "
"achetée pour l'entreprise à des fins personnelles, vous devez payer les "
"taxes que vous aviez initialement déduites en tant que charge "
"professionnelle."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:391
msgid ""
"Odoo may detect that your vendor bill can be interpreted as a document of a "
"type that needs tax integration, as detailed in the :ref:`localizations/"
"italy/document-types` section."
msgstr ""
"Odoo peut détecter que votre facture fournisseur peut être interprétée comme "
"un document d'un type nécessitant une intégration fiscale, comme détaillé "
"dans la section :ref:`localizations/italy/document-types`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:395
msgid ""
"Be sure that you replace the :guilabel:`0% Sale Taxes` on the vendor bill "
"you received with the ones you're supposed to pay to the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia "
"delle Entrate)`. A button then appears on the top of the single vendor bill "
"form to send them."
msgstr ""
"Assurez-vous de remplacer les :guilabel:`0% Sale Taxes` sur la facture "
"fournisseur que vous avez reçue par celles que vous êtes censé payer à "
"l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)`. Un bouton apparaît alors en haut du "
"formulaire de facture fournisseur pour les envoyer."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:399
msgid ""
"When clicking on the :guilabel:`Send Tax Integration` button, an XML file of "
"the appropriate :guilabel:`Document Type` is generated, attached to the "
"bill, and sent as for invoices."
msgstr ""
"En cliquant sur le bouton :guilabel:`Envoyer l'intégration fiscale`, un "
"fichier XML du :guilabel:`Type de document` approprié est généré, joint à la "
"facture fournisseur et envoyé comme pour les factures."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:0
msgid "EDI Send Tax Integration button"
msgstr "Bouton EDI Envoyer l'intégration fiscale"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:408
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:344
msgid "Document Types"
msgstr "Types de documents"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:410
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` requires businesses to send "
"customer invoices and other documents through the :abbr:`EDI (Electronic "
"Data Interchange)`."
msgstr ""
"Le :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` exige des entreprises qu'elles "
"envoient les factures clients et autres documents via l':abbr:`EDI "
"(Electronic Data Interchange)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:413
msgid ""
"The following :guilabel:`Document Type` codes all technically identify "
"different business use cases."
msgstr ""
"Les codes :guilabel:`Type de document` suivants identifient tous "
"techniquement différents cas d'usage métier."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:418
msgid "TD01 - Invoices"
msgstr "TD01 - Factures"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:420
msgid ""
"This represents the standard **domestic** scenario for all invoices "
"exchanged through the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. Any invoice "
"that doesn't fall into one of the specific special cases is categorized as a "
"regular invoice, identified by the :guilabel:`Document Type` `TD01`."
msgstr ""
"Cela représente le scénario **domestique** standard pour toutes les factures "
"échangées via le :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. Toute facture qui ne "
"relève pas de l'un des cas particuliers spécifiques est catégorisée comme "
"une facture régulière, identifiée par le :guilabel:`Document Type` `TD01`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:427
msgid "TD02 - Down payments"
msgstr "TD02 - Acomptes"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:429
msgid ""
"**Down payment** invoices are imported/exported with a "
"different :guilabel:`Document Type` code `TDO2` than regular invoices. Upon "
"import of the invoice, a regular vendor bill is created."
msgstr ""
"Les factures **d'acompte** sont importées/exportées avec un "
"code :guilabel:`Type de document` différent `TDO2` par rapport aux factures "
"classiques. Lors de l'importation de la facture, une facture fournisseur "
"classique est créée."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:432
msgid ""
"Odoo exports transactions as `TD02` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo exporte les transactions en tant que `TD02` si les conditions suivantes "
"sont remplies :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:434
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:574
msgid "It is an invoice;"
msgstr "C'est une facture ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:435
msgid "All invoice lines are related to down payment sales order lines."
msgstr ""
"Toutes les lignes de facture sont liées à des lignes de commande client "
"d'acompte."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:440
msgid "TD04 - Credit notes"
msgstr "TD04 - Notes de crédit"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:442
msgid ""
"It is the standard scenario for all **credit notes** issued to **domestic** "
"clients, when we need to formally acknowledge that the seller is reducing or "
"cancelling a previously issued invoice, for example, in case of overbilling, "
"incorrect items, or overpayment. Just like invoices, they must be sent to "
"the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`, their :guilabel:`Document Type` "
"`TD04`"
msgstr ""
"Il s'agit du scénario standard pour toutes les **notes de crédit** émises à "
"des clients **nationaux**, lorsque nous devons reconnaître formellement que "
"le vendeur réduit ou annule une facture précédemment émise, par exemple, en "
"cas de surfacturation, d'articles incorrects ou de trop-perçu. Tout comme "
"les factures, elles doivent être envoyées au :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`, leur :guilabel:`Type de document` `TD04`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:450
msgid "TD07, TD08, TD09 - Simplified Invoicing"
msgstr "TD07, TD08, TD09 - Facturation simplifiée"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:452
msgid ""
"Simplified invoices (`TD07`), credit notes (`TD08`), and debit notes "
"(`TD09`) can be used to certify domestic transactions under 400 EUR (VAT "
"included). Its status is the same as that of a regular invoice, but with "
"fewer information requirements."
msgstr ""
"Les factures simplifiées (`TD07`), les notes de crédit (`TD08`) et les notes "
"de débit (`TD09`) peuvent être utilisées pour certifier les transactions "
"domestiques de moins de 400 EUR (TVA incluse). Leur statut est le même que "
"celui d'une facture normale, mais avec moins d'exigences d'information."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:456
msgid "For a simplified invoice to be established, it must include:"
msgstr "Pour qu'une facture simplifiée soit établie, elle doit inclure :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:458
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer Invoice` reference: **unique** numbering sequence with "
"**no gaps**;"
msgstr ""
"Référence de la :guilabel:`facture client` : séquence de numérotation "
"**unique** **sans écarts** ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:459
msgid ":guilabel:`Invoice Date`: issue **date** of the invoice;"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Date de facturation` : **date** d'émission de la facture ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:460
msgid ""
":ref:`Company Info <general/companies/company>`: the **seller**'s full "
"credentials (VAT/TIN number, name, full address);"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Informations sur la société <general/companies/company>` : les "
"identifiants complets du **vendeur** (numéro de TVA/TIN, nom, adresse "
"complète) ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:462
msgid ":guilabel:`VAT`: the **buyer**'s VAT/TIN number (on the partner form);"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`TVA` : le numéro de TVA/NIF de l'**acheteur** (sur la fiche du "
"partenaire) ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:463
msgid ":guilabel:`Total`: the total **amount** (VAT included) of the invoice."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Total` : le **montant** total (TVA comprise) de la facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:465
msgid ""
"In the :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)`, Odoo exports invoices as "
"simplified if:"
msgstr ""
"Dans l':abbr:`EDI (Échange de données informatisé)`, Odoo exporte les "
"factures en format simplifié si :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:467
msgid "It is a domestic transaction (i.e., the partner is from Italy);"
msgstr ""
"Il s'agit d'une transaction nationale (c'est-à-dire que le partenaire est "
"d'Italie) ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:468
msgid ""
"Your company's **required fields** (:guilabel:`VAT Number` "
"or :guilabel:`Codice Fiscale`, :guilabel:`Fiscal Regime`, and full "
"**address**) are provided;"
msgstr ""
"Les **champs obligatoires** de votre société (:guilabel:`Numéro de TVA` ou "
":guilabel:`Codice Fiscale`, :guilabel:`Régime fiscal` et **adresse** "
"complète) sont fournis ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:470
msgid ""
"The partner's address is not fully specified (i.e., it misses the City or "
"the ZipCode);"
msgstr ""
"L'adresse du partenaire n'est pas entièrement spécifiée (c'est-à-dire qu'il "
"manque la ville ou le code postal) ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:471
msgid "The total amount of VAT included is **less** than **400 EUR**."
msgstr "Le montant total TVA incluse est **inférieur** à **400 EUR**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:474
msgid ""
"The 400 EUR threshold was defined in `the decree of the 10th of May 2019 in "
"the Gazzetta Ufficiale <https://www.gazzettaufficiale.it/eli/id/"
"2019/05/24/19A03271/sg>`_. We advise you to check the current official value."
msgstr ""
"Le seuil de 400€ a été défini dans `le décret du 10 mai 2019 publié dans la "
"Gazzetta Ufficiale <https://www.gazzettaufficiale.it/eli/id/"
"2019/05/24/19A03271/sg>`_. Nous vous recommandons de vérifier le montant "
"officiel actuel."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:481
msgid "TD16 - Internal Reverse Charge"
msgstr "TD16 - Autoliquidation interne"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:483
msgid ""
"Internal reverse charge transactions (see :ref:`localizations/italy/tax-"
"exemption` and :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`) are exported as "
"`TD16` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Les transactions d'autoliquidation internes (voir :ref:`localizations/italy/"
"tax-exemption` et :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`) sont exportées "
"en tant que `TD16` si les conditions suivantes sont remplies :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:487
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:506
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:522
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:543
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:609
msgid "It is a vendor bill;"
msgstr "Il s'agit d'une facture fournisseur ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:488
msgid ""
"It has at least **one tax** on the invoice lines that targets one of "
"these :ref:`tax grids <localizations/italy/grids>`: `VJ6`, `VJ7`, `VJ8`, "
"`VJ12`, `VJ13`, `VJ14`, `VJ15`, `VJ16`, `VJ17`"
msgstr ""
"Elle comporte au moins **une taxe** sur les lignes de facture qui cible "
"l'une de ces :ref:`grilles de taxe <localizations/italy/grids>` : `VJ6`, "
"`VJ7`, `VJ8`, `VJ12`, `VJ13`, `VJ14`, `VJ15`, `VJ16`, `VJ17`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:494
msgid "TD17 - Buying services from abroad"
msgstr "TD17 - Achat de services à l'étranger"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:496
msgid ""
"When buying **services** from **EU** and **non-EU** countries, the foreign "
"*seller* invoices a service with a **VAT-excluded** price, as it is not "
"taxable in Italy. The VAT is paid by the *buyer* in Italy."
msgstr ""
"Lors de l'achat de **services** auprès de pays de l'**UE** et **hors UE**, "
"le *vendeur* étranger facture un service avec un prix **hors TVA**, car il "
"n'est pas taxable en Italie. La TVA est payée par l'*acheteur* en Italie."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:500
msgid ""
"Within the EU: the *buyer* integrates the invoice received with the **VAT "
"information** due in Italy (i.e., **vendor bill tax integration**);"
msgstr ""
"Au sein de l'UE : l'*acheteur* intègre la facture reçue avec les "
"**informations de TVA** dues en Italie (c'est-à-dire **intégration de la "
"taxe sur la facture fournisseur**) ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:502
msgid ""
"Non-EU: the *buyer* sends themselves an invoice (i.e., **self-billing**)."
msgstr ""
"Non UE : l'*acheteur* s'envoie lui-même une facture (c'est-à-dire **auto-"
"facturation**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:504
msgid ""
"Odoo exports a transaction as `TD17` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo exporte une transaction en tant que `TD17` si les conditions suivantes "
"sont réunies :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:507
msgid ""
"It has at least **one tax** on the invoice lines that targets the tax "
"grid :ref:`VJ3 <localizations/italy/grids>`;"
msgstr ""
"Elle comporte au moins **une taxe** sur les lignes de facture qui cible la "
"grille de taxes :ref:`VJ3 <localizations/italy/grids>` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:509
msgid ""
"All invoice lines either have :guilabel:`Services` as **products**, or a tax "
"with the :guilabel:`Services` as **tax scope**."
msgstr ""
"Toutes les lignes de facture ont des :guilabel:`Services` comme **produits** "
"ou une taxe dont le **champ d'application** inclut les :guilabel:`Services`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:515
msgid "TD18 - Buying goods from EU"
msgstr "TD18 - Achat de biens en provenance de l'UE"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:517
msgid ""
"Invoices issued within the EU follow a **standard format**, therefore only "
"an integration of the existing invoice is required."
msgstr ""
"Les factures émises au sein de l'UE respectent un **format standard**, donc "
"une seule intégration de la facture existante est requise."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:520
msgid ""
"Odoo exports a transaction as `TD18` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo exporte une transaction en tant que `TD18` si les conditions suivantes "
"sont réunies :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:523
msgid "The **partner** is from an **EU** country;"
msgstr "Le **partenaire** provient d'un pays de l'**UE** ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:524
msgid ""
"It has at least one tax on the invoice lines that targets the tax "
"grid :ref:`VJ9 <localizations/italy/grids>`;"
msgstr ""
"Elle comporte au moins une taxe sur les lignes de facture qui cible la "
"grille de taxes :ref:`VJ9 <localizations/italy/grids>` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:526
msgid ""
"All invoice lines either have :guilabel:`Consumable` as **products**, or a "
"tax with :guilabel:`Goods` as **tax scope**."
msgstr ""
"Toutes les lignes de facture ont soit :guilabel:`Consommable` comme "
"**produits**, soit une taxe avec :guilabel:`Marchandises` comme **portée de "
"taxe**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:532
msgid "TD19 - Buying goods from VAT deposit"
msgstr "TD19 - Achat de biens depuis un dépôt de TVA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:534
msgid ""
"Buying **goods** from a **foreign** vendor, but the **goods** are already in "
"**Italy** in a **VAT deposit**."
msgstr ""
"Achat de **marchandises** auprès d'un fournisseur **étranger**, mais les "
"**marchandises** sont déjà en **Italie** dans un **dépôt TVA**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:537
msgid ""
"From the EU: the *buyer* integrates the invoice received with the **VAT "
"information** due in Italy (i.e., **vendor bill tax integration**);"
msgstr ""
"En provenance de l'UE : l'*acheteur* intègre la facture reçue avec les "
"**informations de TVA** dues en Italie (c'est-à-dire **intégration de la "
"taxe sur la facture fournisseur**) ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:539
msgid ""
"Non-EU: the *buyer* sends an invoice to *themselves* (i.e., **self-"
"billing**)."
msgstr ""
"Non UE : l'*acheteur* s'envoie *lui-même* une facture (c'est-à-dire **auto-"
"facturation**)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:541
msgid ""
"Odoo exports a transaction as a `TD19` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo exporte une transaction en tant que `TD19` si les conditions suivantes "
"sont remplies :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:544
msgid ""
"It has at least one tax on the invoice lines that targets the tax "
"grid :ref:`VJ3 <localizations/italy/grids>`;"
msgstr ""
"Elle comporte au moins une taxe sur les lignes de facture qui cible la "
"grille de taxes :ref:`VJ3 <localizations/italy/grids>` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:546
msgid ""
"All invoice lines either have :guilabel:`Consumables` as products, or a tax "
"with :guilabel:`Goods` as **tax scope**."
msgstr ""
"Toutes les lignes de facture ont soit :guilabel:`Consommables` comme "
"produits, soit une taxe avec :guilabel:`Marchandises` comme **portée de "
"taxe**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:552
msgid "TD24 - Deferred invoices"
msgstr "TD24 - Factures différées"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:554
msgid ""
"The **deferred invoice** is an invoice that is **issued at a later time** "
"than the sale of goods or the provision of services. A **deferred invoice** "
"has to be issued at the latest within the **15th day** of the month "
"following the delivery covered by the document."
msgstr ""
"La **facture différée** est une facture qui est **émise à un moment "
"ultérieur** à la vente de marchandises ou à la fourniture de services. Une "
"**facture différée** doit être émise au plus tard le **15ème jour** du mois "
"suivant la livraison ciblée par le document. "

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:558
msgid ""
"It usually is a **summary invoice** containing a list of multiple sales of "
"goods or services carried out in the month. The business is allowed to "
"**group** the sales into **one invoice**, generally issued at the **end of "
"the month** for accounting purposes. Deferred invoices are default for "
"**wholesalers** having recurrent clients."
msgstr ""
"Il s'agit généralement d'une **facture récapitulative** contenant une liste "
"de plusieurs ventes de biens ou services effectuées dans le mois. "
"L'entreprise est autorisée à **regrouper** les ventes en **une seule "
"facture**, généralement émise à la **fin du mois** à des fins comptables. "
"Les factures différées sont par défaut pour les **grossistes** ayant des "
"clients récurrents."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:563
msgid ""
"If the goods are transported by a **carrier**, every delivery has an "
"associated **Documento di Transporto (DDT)**, or **Transport Document**. The "
"deferred invoice **must** indicate the details of all the **DDTs** "
"information for better tracing."
msgstr ""
"Si les marchandises sont transportées par un **transporteur**, chaque "
"livraison est accompagnée d'un **Documento di Transporto (DDT)** ou "
"**Document de transport**. La facture différée **doit** indiquer les détails "
"de toutes les informations du **DDT** pour une meilleure traçabilité."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:568
msgid ""
"E-invoicing of deferred invoices requires the "
"`l10n_it_stock_ddt` :ref:`module <localizations/italy/modules>`. In this "
"case, a dedicated :guilabel:`Document Type` `TD24` is used in the e-invoice."
msgstr ""
"La facturation électronique des factures différées nécessite le :ref:`module "
"<localizations/italy/modules>` `l10n_it_stock_ddt`. Dans ce cas, "
"un :guilabel:`Type de document` dédié `TD24` est utilisé dans la facture "
"électronique."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:572
msgid ""
"Odoo exports transactions as `TD24` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo exporte les transactions en tant que `TD24` si les conditions suivantes "
"sont remplies :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:575
msgid ""
"It is associated with deliveries whose **DDTs** have a **different** date "
"than the issue date of the invoice."
msgstr ""
"Elle est associée à des livraisons dont les **DDT** ont une date "
"**différente** de la date d'émission de la facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:581
msgid "TD28 - San Marino"
msgstr "TD28 - Saint-Marin"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:588
msgid ""
"San Marino and Italy have special agreements on e-invoicing operations. As "
"such, **invoices** follow the regular **reverse charge** rules. You can use "
"the proper :guilabel:`Document Type` depending on the invoice type: `TD01`, "
"`TD04`, `TD05`, `TD24`, `TD25`. Additional requirements are not enforced by "
"Odoo. However, the user is requested by the **State** to:"
msgstr ""
"Saint-Marin et l'Italie ont des accords spéciaux sur les opérations de "
"facturation électronique. Ainsi, les **factures** suivent les règles "
"d'**autoliquidation** habituelles. Vous pouvez utiliser le :guilabel:`Type "
"de document` approprié selon le type de facture : `TD01`, `TD04`, `TD05`, "
"`TD24`, `TD25`. Les exigences supplémentaires ne sont pas imposées par Odoo. "
"Cependant, l'utilisateur est tenu par l'**État** de :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:593
msgid "Select a tax with the :guilabel:`Tax Exemption Kind` set to `N3.3`;"
msgstr ""
"Sélectionner une taxe avec le champ :guilabel:`Type d'exonération de taxe` "
"défini sur `N3.3` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:594
msgid ""
"Use the generic :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` :guilabel:`Destination "
"Code` `2R4GTO8`."
msgstr ""
"Utiliser le :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)` générique :guilabel:`Code "
"de destination` `2R4GTO8`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:596
msgid ""
"The invoice is then routed by a dedicated office in San Marino to the "
"correct business."
msgstr ""
"La facture est ensuite acheminée par un bureau dédié à Saint-Marin vers "
"l'entreprise correcte."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:601
msgid "Vendor Bills"
msgstr "Factures fournisseurs"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:603
msgid ""
"When a **paper bill** is received from San Marino, any Italian company "
"**must** submit that invoice to the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle Entrate)` by "
"indicating the e-invoice's :guilabel:`Document Type` field with the special "
"value `TD28`."
msgstr ""
"Lorsqu'une **facture papier** est reçue de Saint-Marin, toute société "
"italienne **doit** soumettre cette facture à l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia delle "
"Entrate)` en indiquant le champ :guilabel:`Type de document` de la facture "
"électronique avec la valeur spéciale `TD28`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:607
msgid ""
"Odoo exports a transaction as `TD28` if the following conditions are met:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo exporte une transaction en tant que `TD28` si les conditions suivantes "
"sont remplies :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:610
msgid ""
"It has at least one tax on the invoice lines that targets the tax "
"grids :ref:`VJ <localizations/italy/grids>`;"
msgstr ""
"Elle comporte au moins une taxe sur les lignes de facture qui cible les "
"grilles de taxes :ref:`VJ <localizations/italy/grids>` ;"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:612
msgid "The **country** of the partner is **San Marino**."
msgstr "Le **pays** du partenaire est **Saint-Marin**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:617
msgid "Public Administration Businesses (B2G)"
msgstr "Entreprises de l'administration publique (B2G)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:619
msgid ""
":abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` businesses are subjected to more control "
"than private businesses as they handle public money coming from taxpayers. "
"The :abbr:`EDI (Electronic Data Interchange)` process adds some steps to "
"the :ref:`regular one <localizations/italy/e-invoicing-process>`, "
"as :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` businesses can **accept** or "
"**refuse** invoices."
msgstr ""
"Les entreprises :abbr:`PA (Administration Publique)` sont soumises à plus de "
"contrôle que les entreprises privées car elles gèrent l'argent public "
"provenant des contribuables. Le processus :abbr:`EDI (Échange de Données "
"Informatisé)` ajoute quelques étapes au processus :ref:`classique "
"<localizations/italy/e-invoicing-process>`, car les entreprises :abbr:`PA "
"(Administration Publique)` peuvent **accepter** ou **refuser** des factures."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:625
msgid ""
":abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` businesses have a 6-digit "
"long :guilabel:`Destination Code`, also called :abbr:`CUU (Codice Univoco "
"Ufficio)`, that is **mandatory**, **PEC** address cannot be used in this "
"case."
msgstr ""
"Les entreprises :abbr:`PA (Administration Publique)` ont un :guilabel:`Code "
"Destinataire` de 6 chiffres, également appelé :abbr:`CUU (Codice Univoco "
"Ufficio)`, qui est **obligatoire**, l'adresse **PEC** ne peut pas être "
"utilisée dans ce cas."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:630
msgid ""
"`Complete list of businesses that belong to the Public Administration along "
"with their Destination Code <https://www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/portale/web/"
"guest/aree-tematiche/fatturazione-elettronica>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Liste complète des entreprises qui appartiennent à l'Administration "
"publique ainsi que leur code de destination <https://"
"www.agenziaentrate.gov.it/portale/web/guest/aree-tematiche/fatturazione-"
"elettronica>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:636
msgid "CIG, CUP, DatiOrdineAcquisto"
msgstr "CIG, CUP, DatiOrdineAcquisto"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:638
msgid ""
"To ensure the effective traceability of payments by public administrations, "
"electronic invoices issued to public administrations must contain:"
msgstr ""
"Pour garantir la traçabilité effective des paiements par les administrations "
"publiques, les factures électroniques émises aux administrations publiques "
"doivent contenir :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:641
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CIG (Codice Identificativo Gara)`, except in cases of exclusion "
"from traceability obligations provided by law n. 136 of August 13, 2010;"
msgstr ""
"Le :abbr:`CIG (Codice Identificativo Gara)`, sauf dans les cas "
"d'exonérations des obligations de traçabilité prévus par la loi n° 136 du 13 "
"août 2010 ; "

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:643
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)`, in case of invoices related to "
"public works."
msgstr ""
"Le :abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)`, dans le cas de factures relatives "
"aux travaux publics."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:645
msgid ""
"If the XML file requires it, the :abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle Entrate)` can "
"*only* proceed payments of electronic invoices when the XML file contains "
"a :abbr:`CIG (Codice Identificativo Gara)` and :abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di "
"Progetto)`."
msgstr ""
"Si le fichier XML l'exige, l':abbr:`AdE (Agenzia Delle Entrate)` peut "
"*uniquement* procéder aux paiements des factures électroniques lorsque le "
"fichier XML contient un :abbr:`CIG (Codice Identificativo Gara)` et un "
":abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:650
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)` and the :abbr:`CIG (Codice "
"Identificativo Gara)` must be included in one of the `DatiOrdineAcquisto`, "
"`DatiContratto`, `DatiConvenzione`, `DateRicezione`, or "
"`DatiFattureCollegate` XML tags."
msgstr ""
"Le :abbr:`CUP (Codice Unico di Progetto)` et le :abbr:`CIG (Codice "
"Identificativo Gara)` doivent être inclus dans l'une des balises XML "
"`DatiOrdineAcquisto`, `DatiContratto`, `DatiConvenzione`, `DateRicezione` ou "
"`DatiFattureCollegate`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:654
msgid ""
"These correspond to the elements named :guilabel:`CodiceCUP` "
"and :guilabel:`CodiceCIG` of the electronic invoice XML file, whose table "
"can be found on the government `website <http://www.fatturapa.gov.it/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ces éléments correspondent aux champs nommés :guilabel:`CodiceCUP` "
"et :guilabel:`CodiceCIG` du fichier XML de facture électronique, dont le "
"tableau se trouve sur le `site Web <http://www.fatturapa.gov.it/>`_ "
"gouvernemental."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:661
msgid "Split Payment"
msgstr "Paiement scindé"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:663
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Split Payment` mechanism behaves much "
"like :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`."
msgstr ""
"Le mécanisme :guilabel:`Paiement fractionné` fonctionne de manière similaire "
"à :ref:`localizations/italy/reverse-charge`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:666
msgid ""
"When an Italian company bills a :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business "
"- for example, cleaning services for a public building - the :abbr:`PA "
"(Public Administration)` business self-reports the VAT to the Tax Agency "
"themselves, and the vendor just has to select the appropriate tax with the "
"right :guilabel:`Tax Exemption` for their invoice lines."
msgstr ""
"Lorsqu'une entreprise italienne facture une entreprise :abbr:`PA "
"(Administration Publique)` - par exemple, des services de nettoyage pour un "
"bâtiment public - l'entreprise :abbr:`PA (Administration Publique)` auto-"
"déclare la TVA à l'Agence fiscale elle-même, et le vendeur doit simplement "
"sélectionner la taxe appropriée avec l':guilabel:`Exonération fiscale` "
"correcte pour ses lignes de facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:671
msgid ""
"The specific :guilabel:`Scissione dei Pagamenti` fiscal position is "
"available to deal with partners belonging to the :abbr:`PA (Public "
"Administration)`."
msgstr ""
"La position fiscale spécifique :guilabel:`Scissione dei Pagamenti` est "
"disponible pour traiter les partenaires appartenant à l':abbr:`PA "
"(Administration Publique)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:682
msgid "Qualified electronic signature"
msgstr "Signature électronique qualifiée"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:684
msgid ""
"Invoices and bills intended for the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` must "
"include a **qualified electronic signature** when submitted through "
"the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. This signature is automatically "
"applied in the :abbr:`XAdES (XML Advanced Electronic Signature)` format when "
"the invoice's partner has a 6-digit long :guilabel:`Destination Code` (which "
"indicates a :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business)."
msgstr ""
"Les factures et notes de frais destinées à l':abbr:`PA (Administration "
"Publique)` doivent inclure une **signature électronique qualifiée** lors de "
"leur soumission via le :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`. Cette "
"signature est automatiquement appliquée au format :abbr:`XAdES (XML Advanced "
"Electronic Signature)` lorsque le partenaire de la facture possède un "
":guilabel:`Code de destination` de 6 chiffres (ce qui indique une entreprise "
"de type :abbr:`PA (Administration Publique)`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:691
msgid ""
"When such an invoice is transmitted to the Tax Agency, the generated `.xml` "
"file is signed on the Odoo servers, returned to the database, and attached "
"to the invoice automatically."
msgstr ""
"Lorsqu'une telle facture est transmise à l'administration fiscale, le "
"fichier `.xml` généré est signé sur les serveurs Odoo, renvoyé à la base de "
"données et joint automatiquement à la facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:697
msgid "Acceptance or Refusal"
msgstr "Acceptation ou refus"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:699
msgid ""
"After receiving the invoice through the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`, the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business has 15 days "
"to accept the invoice. If it does, then the process ends here. If "
"the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business refuses the invoice, it is "
"still considered valid once it is accepted by the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di "
"Interscambio)`. You then have to issue a credit note to compensate and send "
"it to the :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`."
msgstr ""
"Après réception de la facture via le :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`, "
"l'entreprise :abbr:`PA (Administration Publique)` dispose de 15 jours pour "
"accepter la facture. Si elle le fait, le processus se termine ici. Si "
"l'entreprise :abbr:`PA (Administration Publique)` refuse la facture, elle "
"est toujours considérée comme valide une fois acceptée par le :abbr:`SdI "
"(Sistema di Interscambio)`. Vous devez alors émettre une note de crédit pour "
"compenser et l'envoyer au :abbr:`SdI (Sistema di Interscambio)`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:708
msgid "Expired Terms"
msgstr "Délais expirés"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:710
msgid ""
"If the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business doesn't reply within 15 "
"days, you need to contact the :abbr:`PA (Public Administration)` business "
"directly, sending them both the invoice and the received deadline "
"notification by email. You can make an arrangement with them and manually "
"set the correct :guilabel:`SdI State` on your invoice."
msgstr ""
"Si l'entreprise :abbr:`PA (Administration Publique)` ne répond pas dans les "
"15 jours, vous devez contacter directement l'entreprise :abbr:`PA "
"(Administration Publique)`, en lui envoyant par e-mail à la fois la facture "
"et la notification de délai reçue. Vous pouvez convenir d'un arrangement "
"avec elle et définir manuellement l':guilabel:`État SdI` correct sur votre "
"facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:718
msgid "Point of Sale fiscal printers"
msgstr "Imprimantes fiscales de Point de Vente"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:721
msgid ""
"Fiscal printers are distinct from :doc:`ePOS printers </applications/sales/"
"point_of_sale/configuration/epos_printers>`. The IP address for a fiscal "
"printer should not be entered in the ePOS IP address settings."
msgstr ""
"Les imprimantes fiscales sont distinctes des :doc:`imprimantes ePOS </"
"applications/sales/point_of_sale/configuration/epos_printers>`. L'adresse IP "
"d'une imprimante fiscale ne doit pas être saisie dans les paramètres "
"d'adresse IP ePOS."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:725
msgid ""
"Fiscal regulations mandate using certified RT devices, such as RT printers "
"or RT servers, to ensure compliant sales receipts and secure communication "
"with the Tax Authority. These devices automatically transmit fiscal data "
"daily. RT printers, designed for individual POS terminals, handle "
"transactions, print receipts, and report to the authorities, ensuring data "
"integrity and compliance."
msgstr ""
"La réglementation fiscale impose l'utilisation d'appareils RT certifiés, "
"tels que des imprimantes RT ou des serveurs RT, pour garantir la conformité "
"des reçus de vente et la communication sécurisée avec l'administration "
"fiscale. Ces appareils transmettent automatiquement les données fiscales "
"quotidiennement. Les imprimantes RT, conçues pour les terminaux Point de "
"Vente individuels, gèrent les transactions, impriment les reçus et "
"transmettent les données aux autorités, garantissant ainsi l'intégrité des "
"données et la conformité."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:733
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:57
msgid "Simulation mode"
msgstr "Mode simulation"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:736
msgid ""
"Since the simulation mode sends data to the authorities, it should only be "
"enabled at the very start of the printer's configuration process. Once the "
"printer is switched to the production mode, it cannot be reverted to the "
"simulation mode."
msgstr ""
"Étant donné que le mode simulation envoie des données aux autorités, il ne "
"doit être activé qu'au tout début du processus de configuration de "
"l'imprimante. Une fois l'imprimante basculée en mode production, elle ne "
"peut plus être rétablie en mode simulation."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:740
msgid ""
"To test the fiscal printer setup with Odoo, configure the fiscal printer in "
"the simulation mode as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Pour tester la configuration de l'imprimante fiscale avec Odoo, configurez "
"l'imprimante fiscale en mode simulation comme suit :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:743
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:774
msgid ""
"Make sure the fiscal printer is set to its default state: printer on, start-"
"up cycle complete, and no transaction in progress."
msgstr ""
"Assurez-vous que l'imprimante fiscale est dans son état par défaut : "
"imprimante allumée, cycle de démarrage terminé et aucune transaction en "
"cours."

