msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Validate`. Odoo will generate the EFT file in the "
"chatter. Click on the file to preview or download it."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, cliquer sur :guilabel:`Valider`. Odoo génère le fichier EFT dans le "
