#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:357
msgid ""
"If your business is already up and running with `Employment Hero <https://"
"employmenthero.com/>`_, the connector can be used as an alternative payroll "
"solution."
msgstr ""
"Si votre entreprise est déjà opérationnelle avec `Employment Hero <https://"
"employmenthero.com/>`_, le connecteur peut être utilisé comme solution de "
"paie alternative."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:360
msgid ""
"The Employment Hero module automatically synchronises payslip accounting "
"entries (e.g., expenses, social charges, liabilities, taxes) from "
"**Employment Hero** to Odoo. Payroll administration is still done in "
"**Employment Hero**; only the **journal entries** are recorded in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Le module Employment Hero synchronise automatiquement les écritures "
"comptables des fiches de paie (par exemple, dépenses, charges sociales, "
"passifs, taxes) d'**Employment Hero** vers Odoo. L'administration de la paie "
"est toujours effectuée dans **Employment Hero** ; seules les **écritures "
"comptables** sont enregistrées dans Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/new_zealand.rst:365
msgid ""
"To :ref:`configure the Employment Hero API <employment_hero/configuration>` "
"for **New Zealand**, use the following value as :guilabel:`Payroll URL`: "
"`https://api.nzpayroll.co.nz/`."
msgstr ""
"Pour :ref:`configurer l'API Employment Hero <employment_hero/configuration>` "
"pour la **Nouvelle-Zélande**, utiliser la valeur suivante "
"comme :guilabel:`URL de paie` : `https://api.nzpayroll.co.nz/`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:3
msgid "Oman"
msgstr "Oman"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:10
msgid "The following modules related to the Omani localization are available:"
msgstr ""
"Les modules suivants liés à la localisation omanaise sont disponibles :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:19
msgid ":guilabel:`Oman - Accounting`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Oman - Comptabilité`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:20
msgid "`l10n_om`"
msgstr "`l10n_om`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:21
msgid ""
"Omani :ref:`fiscal localization package <fiscal_localizations/packages>`, "
"complete with the local chart of accounts, taxes, tax report, and fiscal "
"positions."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Package de localisation fiscale <fiscal_localizations/packages>` "
"omanais, comprenant le plan comptable local, les taxes, le rapport fiscal et "
"les positions fiscales."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:23
msgid ":guilabel:`Oman - Accounting Reports`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Oman - Rapports comptables`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:24
msgid "`l10n_om_reports`"
msgstr "`l10n_om_reports`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:25
msgid "Accounting reports for Oman."
msgstr "Rapports comptables pour Oman."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:28
msgid ""
"The module automatically installs core configurations. A manual :doc:`update "
"</applications/general/apps_modules>` may be required for missing elements "
"or updates."
msgstr ""
"Le module installe automatiquement les configurations de base. "
"Une :doc:`mise à jour </applications/general/apps_modules>` manuelle peut "
"être nécessaire pour les éléments manquants ou les mises à jour."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:36
msgid ""
"The Omani localization package provides the necessary accounting setup for "
"companies operating in Oman, including a pre-configured chart of accounts, "
"taxes, fiscal positions, and a standard tax report format. It ensures "
"alignment with Oman VAT regulations and Royal Decree requirements."
msgstr ""
"Le package de localisation omanais fournit la configuration comptable "
"nécessaire pour les entreprises opérant à Oman, incluant un plan comptable "
"préconfiguré, des taxes, des positions fiscales et un format de rapport "
"fiscal standard. Il assure la conformité avec les réglementations TVA d'Oman "
"et les exigences du Décret Royal."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:40
msgid ""
"The Omani localization package provides the following key features to ensure "
"compliance with local fiscal and accounting regulations:"
msgstr ""
"Le package de localisation omanais fournit les fonctionnalités clés "
"suivantes pour assurer la conformité avec les réglementations fiscales et "
"comptables locales :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:43
msgid ""
":ref:`Chart of Accounts <localizations/oman/chart-of-accounts>`: based on "
"Omani standards, with mapped account groups and default account mappings."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Plan comptable <localizations/oman/chart-of-accounts>` : basé sur les "
"normes omanaises, avec groupes de comptes mappés et comptes par défaut "
"configurés."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:45
msgid ""
":ref:`Taxes <localizations/oman/taxes>`: standard 5% VAT, zero-rated "
"domestic as well as exports, exempt, imports, and reverse charge taxes."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Taxes <localizations/oman/taxes>` : TVA standard de 5%, taux zéro "
"domestique ainsi qu'exportations, exonéré, importations et autoliquidation."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:47
msgid ""
":doc:`Fiscal Positions <../accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions>`: automated "
"tax adjustments based on customer or supplier registration status."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Positions fiscales <../accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions>` : "
"ajustements fiscaux automatisés selon le statut d'enregistrement du client "
"ou du fournisseur."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:49
msgid ""
":ref:`Tax Report <localizations/oman/tax-report>`: structured according to "
"the Oman VAT return format, as issued by the Tax Authority."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Rapport fiscal <localizations/oman/tax-report>` : structuré selon le "
"format de déclaration de TVA d'Oman, tel qu'émis par l'Autorité Fiscale."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:57
msgid ""
"The Omani :doc:`chart of accounts <../accounting/get_started/"
"chart_of_accounts>` is based on the local rules and regulations. This "
"includes pre-configured account groups and mapped default accounts. Use "
"the :ref:`predefined structure <chart-of-account/create>` or create new "
"accounts, as needed."
msgstr ""
"Le :doc:`plan comptable <../accounting/get_started/chart_of_accounts>` "
"omanais est basé sur les règles et réglementations locales. Cela inclut des "
"groupes de comptes préconfigurés et des comptes par défaut mappés. Utiliser "
"la :ref:`structure prédéfinie <chart-of-account/create>` ou créer de "
"nouveaux comptes, selon les besoins."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:63
msgid ""
"Accounts are grouped under relevant categories such as assets, liabilities, "
"income, and expenses in line with local standards."
msgstr ""
"Les comptes sont groupés sous les catégories pertinentes telles que les "
"actifs, les passifs, les produits et les charges conformément aux normes "
"locales."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:71
msgid ""
"The following :doc:`Taxes <../accounting/taxes>`, included in the Omani VAT "
"system, are available by default with the Omani localization package:"
msgstr ""
"Les :doc:`taxes <../accounting/taxes>` suivantes, incluses dans le système "
"de TVA omanais, sont disponibles par défaut avec le package de localisation "
"omanais :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:74
msgid ""
"Standard Rate 5%: Applies to the sale of most goods and services within Oman."
msgstr ""
"Taux standard 5% : s'applique à la vente de la plupart des biens et services "
"à Oman."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:75
msgid ""
"Zero-Rated Supplies (0%): Applies to essential supplies where the seller can "
"still reclaim input VAT."
msgstr ""
"Fournitures à taux zéro (0%) : s'applique aux fournitures essentielles pour "
"lesquelles le vendeur peut toujours récupérer la TVA en amont."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:77
msgid ""
"Exports (0%): Applies to the supply of goods and services that are exported "
"outside Oman."
msgstr ""
"Exportations (0%) : s'applique à la fourniture de biens et services exportés "
"hors d'Oman."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:78
msgid ""
"Exempt Supplies: Applies to supplies that are not subject to VAT, and for "
"which the supplier cannot reclaim input VAT on related purchases."
msgstr ""
"Fournitures exonérées : s'applique aux fournitures non soumises à la TVA, et "
"pour lesquelles le fournisseur ne peut pas récupérer la TVA en amont sur les "
"achats liés."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:80
msgid ""
"Reverse Charge Mechanism (RCM): Applies to taxable businesses in Oman "
"receiving services or goods from non-resident suppliers not registered for "
"VAT in Oman."
msgstr ""
"Mécanisme d'autoliquidation (RCM) : s'applique aux entreprises taxables à "
"Oman recevant des services ou des biens de fournisseurs non-résidents non "
"enregistrés à la TVA à Oman."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:82
msgid ""
"Import VAT (5%): Applies to the importation of most goods into Oman, charged "
"at the customs point of entry."
msgstr ""
"TVA à l'importation (5%) : s'applique à l'importation de la plupart des "
"biens à Oman, facturée au point d'entrée douanier."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:90
msgid ""
"The :ref:`VAT return <tax-returns/report>` provides a consolidated overview "
"of the taxable sales and purchases, VAT collected and paid, and the total "
"amount owed or refundable for the reporting period."
msgstr ""
"Le :ref:`rapport de TVA <tax-returns/report>` fournit un aperçu consolidé "
"des ventes et achats imposables, de la TVA collectée et payée, et du montant "
"total dû ou remboursable pour la période de déclaration."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:94
msgid ""
"The tax return aligns with official declarations required by `Oman's Tax "
"Authority <https://tms.taxoman.gov.om/portal/web/taxportal/home>`_."
msgstr ""
"La déclaration fiscale s'aligne avec les déclarations officielles requises "
"par `l'Autorité Fiscale d'Oman <https://tms.taxoman.gov.om/portal/web/"
"taxportal/home>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/oman.rst:96
msgid ""
