"Go to :menuselection:`Contacts --> Configuration --> Bank Accounts` and "
"select the bank account to activate PayNow. Set the :guilabel:`Proxy Type` "
"and fill in the :guilabel:`Proxy Value` field depending on the chosen type."
msgstr ""
"Aller dans :menuselection:`Contacts --> Configuration --> Comptes bancaires` "
"et sélectionner le compte bancaire pour activer PayNow. Définir "
"le :guilabel:`Type de proxy` et remplir le champ :guilabel:`Valeur du proxy` "
