#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:191
msgid ""
"Producers of Veri*Factu billing systems must self-certify their compliance "
"with the regulations. :download:`Download Odoo's \"declaración "
"responsable\"<spain/declaracion_responsable.pdf>`"
