":ref:`Installer <general/install>` le module :guilabel:`Espagne - "
"Veri*Factu` (`l10n_es_edi_verifactu`)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:212
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` "
"or :menuselection:`Invoicing --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu` section, check the :guilabel:`Enable "
"Veri*Factu` option, and click :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Manage "
"certificates` to add a certificate."
msgstr ""
"Aller à :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Configuration --> Paramètres` ou "
":menuselection:`Facturation --> Configuration --> Paramètres`, faire défiler "
"jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Veri\\*Factu`, cocher l'option "
":guilabel:`Activer Veri*Factu`, et cliquer sur :icon:`oi-arrow-right` "
":guilabel:`Gérer les certificats` pour ajouter un certificat."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:216
