"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings` and scroll "
"down to the :guilabel:`Spain Localization` section."
msgstr ""
"Aller à :menuselection:`Comptabilité --> Configuration --> Paramètres` et "
"faire défiler jusqu'à la section :guilabel:`Localisation espagnole`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:304
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Registro de Libros connection TicketBAI` section, select a "
"region in the :guilabel:`Tax Agency for TBAI` field and :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Dans la section :guilabel:`Connexion du registre des livres TicketBAI`, "
