#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:151
msgid "ISO 20022 and SEPA pain versions"
msgstr "Versions ISO 20022 et SEPA pain"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:153
msgid ""
"Switzerland uses a specific, localized version of the :ref:`ISO 20022 "
"<accounting/sepa_payments/iso20022>` format. To configure the appropriate "
"Swiss format, open the **Accounting** app, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Journals`, and open your **bank** "
"journal. Click the :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments` tab, then "
"click :guilabel:`Add a line`, and select :guilabel:`Swiss ISO20022`."
msgstr ""
"La Suisse utilise une version spécifique et localisée du format :ref:`ISO "
"20022 <accounting/sepa_payments/iso20022>`. Pour configurer le format suisse "
"approprié, ouvrir l'application **Comptabilité**, aller à "
":menuselection:`Configuration --> Journaux` et ouvrir votre journal "
"**bancaire**. Cliquer sur l'onglet :guilabel:`Paiements sortants`, puis "
"cliquer sur :guilabel:`Ajouter une ligne` et sélectionner :guilabel:`Swiss "
"ISO20022`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:159
msgid ""
"If you need to make :doc:`SEPA payments <../accounting/payments/"
"sepa_payments>`, you can configure a specific PAIN version. Go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Journals` and open "
"your :guilabel:`Bank` journal. Depending on your configuration needs:"
msgstr ""
"Si vous devez effectuer des :doc:`paiements SEPA <../accounting/payments/"
"sepa_payments>`, vous pouvez configurer une version PAIN spécifique. Aller à "
":menuselection:`Configuration --> Journaux` et ouvrir votre journal "
":guilabel:`Banque`. Selon vos besoins de configuration :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:163
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Incoming Payments` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line`, "
"select a SEPA payment method, and choose a version from the :guilabel:`SEPA "
"Pain Version` field."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur l'onglet :guilabel:`Paiements entrants`, cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`Ajouter une ligne`, sélectionner un mode de paiement SEPA et "
"choisir une version dans le champ :guilabel:`Version SEPA Pain`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:165
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line`, "
"select a SEPA payment method, and choose a version from the :guilabel:`XML "
"Format` field."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur l'onglet :guilabel:`Paiements sortants`, cliquer sur "
":guilabel:`Ajouter une ligne`, sélectionner un mode de paiement SEPA et "
"choisir une version dans le champ :guilabel:`Format XML`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:174
msgid ""
"To set the **PAIN** version used for XML exports, refer to "
"this :ref:`section <switzerland/iso20022>`."
msgstr ""
"Pour définir la version **PAIN** utilisée pour les exports XML, se référer à "
"cette :ref:`section <switzerland/iso20022>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:181
msgid ""
"On the **batch payment creation** screen, before "
"clicking :guilabel:`Validate`, you can define which parties will bear the "
