#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:157
msgid ""
"Select a :ref:`customer <localizations/taiwan/contacts>` of the "
"type :guilabel:`Individual`."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionner un :ref:`client <localizations/taiwan/contacts>` de "
"type :guilabel:`Individu`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:158
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Ecpay` tab, configure delivery options:"
msgstr "Dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Ecpay`, configurer les options de livraison :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:160
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Get Printed Version`: Check this to allow the customer to receive "
"a printable ECPay invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Obtenir la version imprimée` : Cocher cette case pour permettre "
"au client de recevoir une facture ECPay imprimable."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:162
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Love Code`: Enter the Love Code if the customer wishes to donate "
"the invoice to a charity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Love Code` : saisir le Love Code si le client souhaite faire don "
"de la facture à une œuvre caritative."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:164
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Carrier Type`: Select the carrier type if the customer uses a "
"cloud-based carrier, and enter the :guilabel:`Carrier Number` "
"(and :guilabel:`Carrier Number 2`) if required."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Carrier Type` : sélectionner le type de transporteur si le client "
"utilise un transporteur basé sur le cloud, et saisir le :guilabel:`Carrier "
"Number` (et le :guilabel:`Carrier Number 2`) si nécessaire."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:167
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:191
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Confirm` the invoice, and click :guilabel:`Send`. Then, ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Send to Ecpay` checkbox is selected, and "
"click :guilabel:`Send`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Confirmer` la facture et cliquer sur :guilabel:`Envoyer`. "
"Ensuite, s'assurer que la case :guilabel:`Send to Ecpay` est cochée et "
"cliquer sur :guilabel:`Envoyer`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:169
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:193
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Invoice Status`, :guilabel:`Ecpay Invoice Number`, "
"and :guilabel:`Creation Date` in the :guilabel:`Ecpay` tab will update "
"automatically upon successful submission."
msgstr ""
"Le :guilabel:`Invoice Status`, le :guilabel:`Ecpay Invoice Number` et "
"la :guilabel:`Creation Date` dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Ecpay` se mettent à "
"jour automatiquement après une soumission réussie."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:173
msgid "To print or download the ECpay invoice, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Pour imprimer ou télécharger la facture ECpay, suivre ces étapes :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:175
msgid ""
"Make sure the :guilabel:`Get Printed Version` option is checked in "
"the :guilabel:`Ecpay` tab."
msgstr ""
"S'assurer que l'option :guilabel:`Get Printed Version` est cochée dans "
"l'onglet :guilabel:`Ecpay`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:176
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:203
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-cog` (gear) icon and select :guilabel:`Print Ecpay "
"invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur l'icône :icon:`fa-cog` et sélectionner :guilabel:`Print Ecpay "
