#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:177
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Print Ecpay Invoice` window, select a :guilabel:`Print "
"Format (B2C)` and click :guilabel:`Print Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Dans la fenêtre :guilabel:`Print Ecpay Invoice`, sélectionner "
"un :guilabel:`Print Format (B2C)` et cliquer sur :guilabel:`Print Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:183
msgid "B2B invoice (company)"
msgstr "Facture B2B (entreprise)"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:185
msgid "To send a B2B invoice, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Pour envoyer une facture B2B, suivre ces étapes :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:189
msgid ""
"Select a :ref:`customer <localizations/taiwan/contacts>` who is either "
"a :guilabel:`Company` or an :guilabel:`Individual` belonging to "
"a :guilabel:`Company`."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionner un :ref:`client <localizations/taiwan/contacts>` qui est soit "
"une :guilabel:`Company`, soit un :guilabel:`Individual` appartenant à "
"une :guilabel:`Company`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:197
msgid ""
"Ensure the :guilabel:`Tax ID` field  of the :ref:`customer <localizations/"
"taiwan/contacts>` is filled in with the Tax Identification Number."
msgstr ""
"S'assurer que le champ :guilabel:`Tax ID` du :ref:`client <localizations/"
"taiwan/contacts>` est rempli avec le numéro d'identification fiscale."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:201
msgid ""
"By default, B2B ECpay invoices are available to print or download. Please "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Par défaut, les factures ECpay B2B sont disponibles à l'impression ou au "
"téléchargement. Suivre ces étapes :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:204
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Print Ecpay Invoice` window, select a :guilabel:`Print "
"Format (B2B)` and click :guilabel:`Print Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Dans la fenêtre :guilabel:`Print Ecpay Invoice`, sélectionner "
"un :guilabel:`Print Format (B2B)` et cliquer sur :guilabel:`Print Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:208
msgid ""
"Check the invoice's :guilabel:`Log Note` for ECPay submission details. "
"Failed attempts display error messages, while successful submissions record "
"the :guilabel:`Ecpay invoice number` and :guilabel:`Invoice status`."
msgstr ""
"Consulter la :guilabel:`Log Note` de la facture pour les détails de "
"soumission ECPay. Les tentatives échouées affichent des messages d'erreur, "
"tandis que les soumissions réussies enregistrent le :guilabel:`Ecpay invoice "
"number` et le :guilabel:`Invoice status`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:215
msgid "Invoice Cancellation"
msgstr "Annulation de facture"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:217
msgid "To cancel a submitted invoice:"
msgstr "Pour annuler une facture soumise :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:219
msgid "Open the relevant invoice and click :guilabel:`Request Cancel`."
msgstr "Ouvrir la facture concernée et cliquer sur :guilabel:`Request Cancel`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:220
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, provide a cancellation :guilabel:`Reason`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Cancel Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Dans la fenêtre contextuelle, fournir un motif "
"d'annulation :guilabel:`Reason`, puis cliquer sur :guilabel:`Cancel Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:222
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Invoice Status` changes to :guilabel:`Invalid`, and "
"the :guilabel:`Invalidate Reason` is filled in with the "
"cancellation :guilabel:`Reason`."
msgstr ""
"Le :guilabel:`Invoice Status` passe à :guilabel:`Invalid`, et le "
"champ :guilabel:`Invalidate Reason` est rempli avec le motif "
"d'annulation :guilabel:`Reason`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:0
msgid "ECPay invoice cancellation"
msgstr "Annulation de facture ECPay"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:231
msgid "Send credit notes to ECPay"
msgstr "Envoyer des notes de crédit à ECPay"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:233
msgid ""
"Before sending a credit note, the original invoice must be successfully "
"submitted to ECPay."
msgstr ""
"Avant d'envoyer une note de crédit, la facture originale doit être soumise "
"avec succès à ECPay."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:236
msgid "The credit note amount cannot exceed the original invoice amount."
msgstr ""
"Le montant de la note de crédit ne peut pas dépasser le montant de la "
"facture originale."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:241
msgid "B2C Credit Notes"
msgstr "Notes de crédit B2C"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:243
msgid "To send a B2C credit note to ECPay, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Pour envoyer une note de crédit B2C à ECPay, suivre ces étapes :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:245
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Credit Note` on the relevant invoice and enter "
"the :guilabel:`Reason displayed on Credit Note`."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur :guilabel:`Note de crédit` sur la facture concernée et saisir "
"le :guilabel:`Motif affiché sur la note de crédit`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:247
msgid ""
"Select the :guilabel:`Agreement Type` and the :guilabel:`Allowance Notify "
"Way`, and click :guilabel:`Reverse`."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionner le :guilabel:`Type d'accord` et le :guilabel:`Mode de "
"notification de remise`, puis cliquer sur :guilabel:`Contrepasser`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:249
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:267
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm`, then :guilabel:`Send`, ensuring :guilabel:`Send "
"to Ecpay (Issue Allowance)` is selected."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur :guilabel:`Confirmer`, puis :guilabel:`Envoyer`, en s'assurant "
"que :guilabel:`Envoyer à Ecpay (émettre une remise)` est sélectionné."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:252
msgid ""
"Then, The :guilabel:`Refund State` updates to :guilabel:`Agreed` "
"(for :guilabel:`Offline agreements`) or :guilabel:`To be agreed` "
"(for :guilabel:`Online agreements`). Additionally, the :guilabel:`Refund "
"Invoice Number`, :guilabel:`Refund invoice Agreement Type` "
"and :guilabel:`Allowance Notify Way` updates accordingly in "
"the :guilabel:`Ecpay` tab."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, l':guilabel:`État de remboursement` se met à jour "
"vers :guilabel:`Accepté` (pour les :guilabel:`Accords hors ligne`) "
"ou :guilabel:`À accepter` (pour les :guilabel:`Accords en ligne`). De plus, "
"le :guilabel:`Numéro de facture de remboursement`, le :guilabel:`Type "
"d'accord de facture de remboursement` et le :guilabel:`Mode de notification "
"de remise` se mettent à jour en conséquence dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Ecpay`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:261
msgid "B2B credit notes"
msgstr "Notes de crédit B2B"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:263
msgid "To send a B2B credit note to ECPay, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Pour envoyer une note de crédit B2B à ECPay, suivre ces étapes :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:265
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Credit Note` on the relevant invoice, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Reason displayed on Credit Note`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Reverse`."
msgstr ""
"Cliquer sur :guilabel:`Note de crédit` sur la facture concernée, saisir "
"le :guilabel:`Motif affiché sur la note de crédit`, puis cliquer "
"sur :guilabel:`Contrepasser`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:270
msgid ""
"Then the :guilabel:`Refund Invoice Number` is updated automatically in "
"the :guilabel:`Ecpay` tab."
msgstr ""
"Ensuite, le :guilabel:`Numéro de facture de remboursement` est mis à jour "
"automatiquement dans l'onglet :guilabel:`Ecpay`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:282
msgid "To enable direct invoice submission via eCommerce:"
msgstr "Pour activer la soumission directe des factures via eCommerce :"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:284
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr "Aller à :menuselection:`Site Web --> Configuration --> Paramètres`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:285
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Invoicing` section, enable :guilabel:`Automatic Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Dans la section :guilabel:`Facturation`, activer :guilabel:`Facture "
"automatique`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:287
msgid ""
"This ensures invoices are generated and sent to ECPay automatically once the "
"online payment is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Cela garantit que les factures sont générées et envoyées à ECPay "
"automatiquement une fois le paiement en ligne confirmé."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:293
msgid "Checkout Process"
msgstr "Processus de paiement"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:295
msgid ""
"**B2C Customers**: During checkout, customers must indicate whether they "
"want to receive a physical invoice using the :guilabel:`Request a paper "
"copy` field"
msgstr ""
"**Clients B2C** : lors du paiement, les clients doivent indiquer s'ils "
"souhaitent recevoir une facture papier en utilisant le "
"champ :guilabel:`Demander une copie papier`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:298
msgid ":guilabel:`No`: No copy is provided."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Non` : Aucune copie n'est fournie."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:299
msgid ":guilabel:`Yes`: The invoice can be downloaded from the invoice view."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Oui` : La facture peut être téléchargée depuis la vue de facture."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/taiwan.rst:301
msgid ""
"**B2B Customers**: An :guilabel:`Invoicing Info` page appears after delivery "
"confirmation. Customers can either select the :guilabel:`Donate` checkbox to "
"donate the invoice, or choose an :guilabel:`Ecpay e-invoice carrier` from "
"the following options, and provide the :guilabel:`Carrier Number` "
"and :guilabel:`Carrier Number 2` where applicable."
msgstr ""
"**Clients B2B** : Une page :guilabel:`Informations de facturation` apparaît "
"après confirmation de la livraison. Les clients peuvent soit cocher la "
"case :guilabel:`Donner` pour faire don de la facture, soit choisir "
"un :guilabel:`transporteur de facture électronique Ecpay` parmi les options "
"suivantes et fournir le :guilabel:`Numéro de transporteur` et "
"le :guilabel:`Numéro de transporteur 2` le cas échéant."

