#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/uruguay.rst:98
msgid ""
"Open the generated PDF to get the *DGI Main Branch Code* from "
"the :guilabel:`Domicilio Fiscal Número de Local` section."
msgstr ""
"Ouvrez le PDF généré pour obtenir le *code de l'établissement principal DGI* "
